  </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Nëse ndiqni tendencat më të fundit të teknologjisë, do e mendoni vazhdimisht pyetjen se si duket faqja juaj Web ne krahasim me miliona faqe të tjera. Cdo biznes synon rritjen e të ardhurave dhe zhvillimin e identitetit të markës sëtij. Një faktor kyç në marketing është sigurisht faqja e internetit e kompanisë suaj si dhe sistemi i saj i menaxhimit. Duke pasë parasysh shifrat, sistemi WordPress aktualisht mbizotëron tregun, megjithatë, TYPO3 po merr gjithashtu një rol dominues. Në dilemën mes TYPO3 dhe WordPress, stafi i W3DEVELOPMENT ju ofron një zgjidhje optimale të sistemit CMS, bazuar në kërkesat tuaja.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">27</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=17</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',217,'a:11:{s:5:\"CType\";s:20:\"fluidcontent_content\";s:14:\"tx_fed_fcefile\";s:21:\"Theme:BlogTeaser.html\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125901;s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1303:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">TYPO3 vs Wordpress</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Are you following the new trends and technologies and always asking how is your website compared to millions of others? Everyone is struggling with increasing revenue and developing its brand identity. A key factor in the market is, of course, the website of your company, and its content management system. Tracing the run of website market, WordPress has already been in the foreground, however, TYPO3 is also taking respectful place currently. In the competition TYPO3 vs WordPress, our team tries to offer an optimal solution for our clients by choosing the CMS according to their requirements.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">27</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=17</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;}',217,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(323,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,214,1613898980,1532521450,5,0,0,2104,'theme_blogteaser','','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125902,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Modele të dizajnit Responsive Web</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">5 modelet më të njohura të dizajnit Responsive Web\n\nGjithnjë e më shumë përdorues kërkojnë në web duke përdorur pajisje të llojeve të ndryshme. Ato ndryshojnë në madhësi, duke nisur nga ekrani në laptop madhesinë e ekranit të Smartphone. Projektimi i faqes Web bëhet i vështirë, sepse duhen pasë parasysh të gjitha këto lloje të ndryshme ekranesh.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">26</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=16</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',214,'a:11:{s:5:\"CType\";s:20:\"fluidcontent_content\";s:14:\"tx_fed_fcefile\";s:21:\"Theme:BlogTeaser.html\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125902;s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1031:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Web Design Patterns</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Nowadays, more and more users browse the web using different devices, in different screens. They vary in size, from desktop screen to tablet and Smartphone screen. The web development becomes difficult, assuming all these different options in size. By following some web design patterns, the workflow is kept more manageable.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">26</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=16</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;}',214,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(324,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,208,1613898985,1532521450,5,0,0,2055,'theme_blogteaser','','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125903,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">7 Arsyet pse ju duhet të keni një faqe interneti.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Cdo ditë e më tepër rritet numri i njerëzve që përdorin internetin.\nPër cdo informacion që iu nevojitet, ata do e kërkojnë në internet.\nMe zhvillimin e teknologjisë dhe internetit, ju duhet t\'i shikoni të gjithë si klientë potencial. Të rinjtë sot kërkojnë në internet edhe për gjërat që blejnë ose shërbimet që u nevojiten.\nPrandaj është krejt e natyrshme që konsumatorët të mendojnë se çdo biznes është i pranishëm në ueb, në faqen e vet të internetit. Të qenit aktiv në mediat sociale është njëra anë. Gjithashtu, duhet një faqe interneti ku ndjekësit mund të blejnë produktin tuaj ose mund të kërkojnë më shumë detaje për shërbimet tuaja.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">23</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=13</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',208,'a:11:{s:5:\"CType\";s:20:\"fluidcontent_content\";s:14:\"tx_fed_fcefile\";s:21:\"Theme:BlogTeaser.html\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125903;s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1303:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">7 reasons why your business needs a website</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">The number of people that are using the internet is increasing each day. If they need information, they will search it on the Internet. In this technologic era, you should see all of them as potential customers, as they will search on the web even for the things they buy or services they need. Having a website is so normal that customers suppose every business is present on the web on its own website. Being active in the social media is one side, but you also need a website where the followers can purchase your product or can search for more details of your services.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">23</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=13</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',208,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(325,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,209,1613898996,1532521450,5,0,0,2528,'theme_blogteaser','','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125901,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">9 tendencat e dizajnit web për vitin 2018</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Ekspertët e dizajn në web përballen me sfidat teknike por edhe vazhdojnë të krijojnë faqe të thjeshta për përdoruesin, elegante dhe të përshtatshme me çdo pajisje mobile.Në vitin 2017 ka avancuar shumë përdorimi i faqeve të internetit në paisjet mobile. Aktualisht, lundrimi në aplikacione web mobile numëron më shumë përdorues sesa lundrimi në web nga kompjuter apo laptop. Kjo është një nga arsyet pse viti 2018 do të sjellë funksionalitete dhe mënyra të reja për paisjet mobile. Në vazhdim përmenden disa tendenca të dizajnit web për vitin 2018.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">24</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=14</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',209,'a:11:{s:5:\"CType\";s:20:\"fluidcontent_content\";s:14:\"tx_fed_fcefile\";s:21:\"Theme:BlogTeaser.html\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125901;s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1218:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">9 web design trends in 2018</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Web designers deal with the technical challenges, which are large in number. But they still continue to create user-friendly sites, stylish and flexible with every device and just beautiful all at once. 2017 made more advancement in mobile browsing, who now counts more users than desktop browsing. This is a reason why 2018 is going to have fully mobile functionalities in new ways. Meanwhile, desktops will evolve in such way to stay relevant. So, let’s take a look at some web design trends in 2018.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">24</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=14</value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:1