ents. It is called Shopify.</p>\r\n<p>If you own a business, you may have an existing e-commerce store or are looking to expand into this area, you’re probably wondering what the best e-Commerce platform to use in 2019? According to Google Trends, while comparing, Shopify vs Magento, Shopify looks more popular compared to Magento.<br /> Actually,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.shopify.com/free-trial?ref=wbe&amp;subid1=vsMagento&amp;subid2=23f8b8601d23ad4c1d3fc0ad2e001424\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Shopify</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://magento.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Magento</a>&nbsp;are two of the most popular e-commerce platforms on the market. They differ a lot from each other. In the end of this guide, you’ll have a much clear idea to choose, which is the right e-commerce platform for your online store.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:23:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(359,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,359,1580827969,1580827969,13,0,0,6144,'textpic','The main differences','','','<p>Shopify is commercial,&nbsp;a software-as-a-service (SAAS), so users pay a monthly fee to get its services.&nbsp;&nbsp;Magento is free and open source software. Shopify is hosted by its own host, which makes easier the setup and configurations. Magento is hosted by your hosting. The installation and configuration need web programming skills. At the end of the setup, you can start building the online store.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(360,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,360,1580890730,1580890730,13,0,0,6400,'textpic','The easy platform','','','<p>Starting a new business is not easy. At least, the platform of the web store should be easy and helpful. If you choose a platform that adds stress in your work, then you should not focus on your own products and sales, but in the store itself. You better build your store in a platform you soon master and in which you are comfortable with.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify gives you the interactive way to build the website just by drag and drop the elements in the interface. You can set up the store just by moving the components in the way you like to arrange them, so you can quickly start selling. The process of adding new images to the store makes it unique and personalized. Also, the process of setting up the payment method is so easy so you can soon start making money, without worrying about the procedures.&nbsp;Beginners will find Shopify easy to use.</p>\r\n<p>Although very flexible Magento is more complex to use than Shopify. You should learn some technical terms and some code before start selling at a Magento store. Magento platform is less user-friendly and the process of setting up the store requires to navigate is some blocks before becoming a seller. Magento is powerful for experienced users, but a bit difficult for the beginners. This means you need some professional tricks to manage the full functionality it offers.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(361,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1559406812,1544252008,1,0,0,6656,'textpic','More Apps means more functions','','','<p>Both Shopify and Magento have a huge number of main functions, which cover important tasks like marketing, inventory, finance, etc. But for any specific tool, you need to install a new app or an extension of your store. Such software helps you in adding extra functionality and to speed any procedure so you can focus on sales and not on the online store itself.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store offers more than 2 300 applications, free and paid. You can install them by just clicking on it, and personalize it. Some useful apps are those who integrate your store with social media, or with your email. Such connections will increase dramatically the sales of your online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace has over 3 000 extensions, free or paid. Some of them require few coding skills to insert them in the online store and to personalize them. But to us, Magento seems powerful in the wide range of extra functions and in the extensions it offers. Practically, you can do quite everything with Magento extensions, and all you need is to choose the right one and to know how to use it properly.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(362,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,362,1580891157,1580891157,13,0,0,6912,'textpic','Your budget, a key factor','','','<p>The budget is crucial aspect to consider when choosing an e-commerce platform. Shopify and Magento differ in their fees and in their operating costs. Shopify comes with a monthly fee, but it includes the host fee and maintenance service fee. Each premium application has an extra monthly fee.</p>\r\n<p>Magento is a free and open source software but it does not include the cost of hosting. Many Magento apps have fees and in an overall overview, you will need to consult to a web developer to integrate and to configure the Magento apps.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(363,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,363,1580891717,1580891717,13,0,0,7168,'textpic','The size of the store will make you decide','','','<p>Shopify and Magento both are powerful eCommerce platforms, you can make the choice between Shopify vs Magento, based on the size of your business. Shopify offers the Shopify Lite which allow you to sell via Facebook. It also offers three packages: Basic Shopify, Advanced Shopify, and Shopify Plus. Shopify it’s easy to use with a great customer service.</p>\r\n<p>You can choose them depending on your needs and your budget. If you own a small business, Shopify is a promising eCommerce platform.</p>\r\n<p>Magento, on the other hand, is built on an open-source framework, it’s offers the Community package as the right platform for small online shops and the Enterprise package for larger online brands. It has a large extensions marketplace that enables more features for your site and is a platform that prides on its extraordinary scalability for complex and long-term operations.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(364,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1548606057,1544252968,1,0,0,7424,'textpic','Hosting the online store','','','<p>The process of setting up the host in a Shopify store is easy because the whole process can last few minutes, and Shopify provides you the complete solution for hosting your online store. Meanwhile, Magento gives you the responsibility of hosting, downloading, installing and setting up the platform for the new store.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(365,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1548606077,1544253013,1,0,0,7680,'text','The everyday Store Management','','','<p>As soon as you set up your online store, you should add or update product details and manage the inventory. Both Shopify and Magento have a product section which enables the seller to manage to products. If you are not an IT or Web specialist, Shopify is the easiest platform to manage your online store, because of its user-friendly interface.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:23:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(366,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,366,1580892183,1580892183,13,0,0,7936,'textpic','Best for SEO','','','<p>According to statistics, 93% of all website visits start with an online search. Ranking your page high on the list of relevance for a particular search term can be more important and useful than any form of advertising. The best shop is those who have customers shopping there. Both platforms offer good deliver traffic, which is translated as good SEO (search engine optimization) to deliver traffic.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,10,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(367,19,0,0,0,0,0,1581950618,0,367,1580892347,1580892347,13,0,0,8192,'textpic','Themes for a stylish shop','','','<p>When your customers visit your website, the theme of your e-Commerce website will create the first impression.<br /> In both platforms, Shopify and Magento, the look and feel of the store are created by themes.</p>\r\n<p>In both platforms, Shopify and Magento, the look and feel of the store are created by themes. Some of their most basic themes are free. Themes with attractive features are in a symbolic price. If you want a classic image of your store, Magento has lots of such themes. If you want a different image of your store, Shopify themes are better from a design view.</p>\r\n<p>From the technical point, Shopify themes are easier in installation and in modification than the Magento themes.</p>\r\n<p>From the design and the UX aspect, Shopify offers the best-looking themes, without any doubt.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(368,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1548606141,1544253156,1,0,0,8448,'text','Point Of Sale','','','<p>It is an important key solution the web platform offers to the point of sale. Shopify offers a Point of Sale app that runs on any mobile or desktop device and accepts credit card payment. Magento also offers Point of Sales options which are extensions in the marketplace.<br /> <br /> &nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:23:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(369,19,0,0,0,0,0,1582036416,0,369,1582034432,1582034432,13,0,0,8704,'textpic','So which one should you choose?','','','<p>Both Shopify and Magento are powerful e-commerce platforms. Shopify is far easier and fully managed system. Meanwhile, Magento is costless and more complex regarding the installations and customizations.</p>\r\n<p>We cannot define which is the only one choice, to all the stores and business managers that are such differences in needs and in the way they see their business. But as the last suggestion, here are some fantastic Shopify store and some examples of Magento Stores <a href=\"https://w3development.net/work/\" target=\"_blank\">https://w3development.net/work/</a>.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(370,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,358,1552466071,1544253472,1,0,0,3072,'text','Shopify apo Magento','','','<p>Deri pak vite më parë, platforma kryesore e shitjeve online kishte emrin Magento. Por kohët e fundit, një tjetër platformë është e preferuara e shumë shitësve dhe klientëve. Ajo quhet Shopify.</p>\r\n<p>Në të vërtetë, Shopify dhe Magento janë dy nga platformat më të njohura të shitjeve online. Ata ndryshojnë shumë nga njëra-tjetra. Në këtë artikull dalin në pah këto dallime, në mënyrë që ju të vendosni vetë se cila është platforma më e përshtatshme për dyqan tuaj online.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',358,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:18:\"Shopify vs Magento\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:480:\"<p>A few years ago, the market of the e-commerce platforms was mainly called Magento. But recently, a different way of setting up an online store is attracting both sellers and clients. It is called Shopify.</p>\r\n<p>Actually, Shopify and Magento are two of the most popular e-commerce platforms on the market. They differ a lot from each other. In this article, these differences are highlighted, so you can decide which is the right e-commerce platform for your online store.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',358,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(371,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,359,1566571710,1544253472,1,0,0,3328,'textpic','Dallimet kryesore','','','<p>Shopify është me pagesë. Ju duhet të paguani një tarifë mujore për të marrë shërbimet e saj. Magento është softuer falas dhe me kod të hapur.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify është më i lehtë në konfigurim dhe në host-im. Magento-n do e host-oni ju vetë. Instalimi dhe konfigurimi i një dyqani në Magento kërkojnë aftësi programimi në Web. Pasi të përfundoni proçesin e konfigurimit, ju mund të filloni ndërtimin e dyqanit tuaj online.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',359,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"The main differences\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:370:\"<p>Shopify is commercial. You should pay a monthly fee to get its services. Magento is free and open source software. Shopify is hosted by its own host, which makes easier the setup and configurations. Magento is hosted by your hosting. The installation and configuration need web programming skills. At the end of the setup, you can start building the online store.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',359,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(372,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,360,1566571789,1544253472,1,0,0,3584,'textpic','Platforma më e lehtë','','','<p>Nisja e një biznesi të ri nuk është aspak e lehtë. Prandaj të paktën platforma e dyqanit online duhet na vihet në ndihmë. Nëse zgjidhni një platformë që shton stres në punën tuaj, atëherë nuk do mund të përqendroheni në produktet dhe në shitjet tuaja, por në vetë dyqanin. Më mirë ndërtojeni dyqanin tuaj në një platformë të thjeshtë dhe të dobishme.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify ofron një mënyrë interaktive për të ndërtuar faqen e internetit. Ju mund të krijoni listën e produkteve vetëm duke lëvizur komponentët, duke i sistemuar sipas dëshirës.Në këtë mënyrë, ju mund të filloni shpejt shitjen e artikujve. Dyqani bëhet me unik dhe i personalizuar duke shtuar imazhe të reja. Gjithashtu, procesi i përcaktimit të mënyrës së pagesës është kaq i lehtë, sa që shumë shpejt ju mund të filloni të bëni para, pa u shqetësuar për procedurat.</p>\r\n<p>Krijimi i një dyqani me Magento është pak më ndryshe. Ju duhet të mësoni paraprakisht disa terma teknike dhe disa instruksione para se të filloni shitjet. Proçesi i krijimit të dyqanit kërkon të përcaktimin e disa parametrave para se të bëheni shitës. Magento është platformë e fuqishme për përdoruesit me përvojë, por pak e vështirë për fillestarët. Kjo do të thotë që keni nevojë për disa aftësi programimi për të menaxhuar funksionalitetin e plotë që ajo ofron.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',360,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"The easy platform\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1270:\"<p>Starting a new business is not easy. At least, the platform of the web store should be easy and helpful. If you choose a platform that adds stress in your work, then you should not focus on your own products and sales, but in the store itself. You better build your store in a platform you soon master and in which you are comfortable with.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify gives you the interactive way to build the website just by drag and drop the elements in the interface. You can set up the store just by moving the components in the way you like to arrange them, so you can quickly start selling. The process of adding new images to the store makes it unique and personalized. Also, the process of setting up the payment method is so easy so you can soon start making money, without worrying about the procedures.</p>\r\n<p>The beginning with Magento is a bit different. You should learn some technical terms and some code before start selling at a Magento store. Magento platform is less user-friendly and the process of setting up the store requires to navigate is some blocks before becoming a seller. Magento is powerful for experienced users, but a bit difficult for the beginners. This means you need some professional tricks to manage the full functionality it offers.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',360,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(373,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,361,1552464924,1544253472,1,0,0,3840,'textpic','\"Më shumë App\" do të thotë \"Më shumë mundësi\"','','','<p>Të dy, edhe Shopify edhe Magento, ofrojnë një numër të konsiderueshëm funksionalitetesh, të cilat mbulojnë detyra të rëndësishme si marketing, inventar, financë, etj. Por, për çdo funksion shtesë, ju duhet të instaloni një aplikacion të ri ose Extension në dyqanin tuaj. Një softuer i tillë ju ndihmon në shtimin e funksionalitetit shtesë.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store ofron më shumë se 2300 aplikacione, me ose pa pagesë. Ju mund t\'i instaloni ato me një klik të vetëm, dhe me pas ti personalizoni sipas dyqanit tuaj online. Disa aplikacione të dobishme janë ata që integrojnë dyqanin tuaj me mediat sociale, ose me email-in tuaj. Lidhje të tilla do të rrisin ndjeshëm shitjet e artikujve.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace ka mbi 3000 Extensions, me ose pa pagesë. Disa prej tyre kërkojnë pak aftësi programimi, për t\'i integruar dhe për t\'i personalizuar ato. Por për mendimin e ekspertëve tanë, Magento është shumë i fuqishëm për vetë gamën e gjerë të funksioneve që ajo ofron, si dhe për listën e Extensions. Praktikisht, ju mund të bëni gjithçka me Extensions në Magento. Gjithçka që ju duhet është të zgjidhni Extension e duhur dhe të dini se si ta përdorni siç duhet.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',361,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"More Apps means more functions\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1097:\"<p>Both Shopify and Magento have a huge number of main functions, which cover important tasks like marketing, inventory, finance, etc. But for any specific tool, you need to install a new app or an extension of your store. Such software helps you in adding extra functionality and to speed any procedure so you can focus on sales and not on the online store itself.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store offers more than 2 300 applications, free and paid. You can install them by just clicking on it, and personalize it. Some useful apps are those who integrate your store with social media, or with your email. Such connections will increase dramatically the sales of your online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace has over 3 000 extensions, free or paid. Some of them require few coding skills to insert them in the online store and to personalize them. But to us, Magento seems powerful in the wide range of extra functions and in the extensions it offers. Practically, you can do quite everything with Magento extensions, and all you need is to choose the right one and to know how to use it properly.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',361,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(374,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,362,1566577260,1544253472,1,0,0,4096,'textpic','Buxheti juaj: një faktor kyç','','','<p>Buxheti është një faktor që duhet marrë parasysh në zgjedhjen e platformës për shitjet online. Shopify dhe Magento ndryshojnë në tarifat dhe në shpenzimet operative. Shopify është kundrejt një tarife mujore, e cila përfshin tarifën e host-imit dhe tarifën e shërbimit të mirëmbajtjes. Gjithashtu, çdo aplikacion në nivel Premium ka një tarifë shtesë mujore.</p>\r\n<p>Magento është një softuer pa pagese dhe me kod të hapur, por nuk përfshin koston e host-imit. Shumë Extensions në Magento kanë kosto, prandaj ju duhet të konsultoheni me një zhvillues web për të integruar dhe konfiguruar këto aplikacione.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',362,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Your budget, a key factor\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:537:\"<p>The budget is a factor you should consider in choosing the web platform. Shopify and Magento differ in their fees and in their operating costs. Shopify comes with a monthly fee, but it includes the host fee and maintenance service fee. Each premium application has an extra monthly fee.</p>\r\n<p>Magento is a free and open source software but it does not include the cost of hosting. Many Magento apps have fees and in an overall overview, you will need to consult to a web developer to integrate and to configure the Magento apps.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',362,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(375,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,363,1552464952,1544253472,1,0,0,4352,'textpic','Madhësia e dyqanit ju çon drejt zgjedhjes','','','<p>Ju mund të bëni zgjedhjen midis Shopify apo Magento, bazuar në madhësinë e biznesit tuaj. Shopify ofron linjën Shopify Lite, e cila ju lejon të shisni nëpërmjet Facebook-ut. Gjithashtu ofron tre paketa: Basic Shopify, Advanced Shopify dhe Shopify Plus. Mund t\'i zgjidhni ato në varësi të nevojave tuaja dhe buxhetit tuaj. Për një fillim më të mirë zgjidhni Advanced Shopify, sepse përmban shumë opsione të vlefshme për të filluar një dyqan online.</p>\r\n<p>Magento ofron paketën Community, si platformën e duhur për dyqanet e vogla online. Gjithashtu, ajo ofron dhe paketën e Enterprise për bizneset e mëdha.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',363,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:42:\"The size of the store will make you decide\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:562:\"<p>You can make the choice between Shopify vs Magento, based on the size of your business. Shopify offers the Shopify Lite which allow you to sell via Facebook. It also offers three packages: Basic Shopify, Advanced Shopify, and Shopify Plus. You can choose them depending on your needs and your budget. For a startup better choose Advanced Shopify. It contains a whole set of features to initialize an online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento offers the Community package as the right platform for small online shops and the Enterprise package for large online brands.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',363,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(376,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,364,1566577339,1544253472,1,0,0,4608,'textpic','Host-imi i dyqanit online','','','<p>Në Shopify, procesi i host-imit i një dyqani është i lehtë, sepse zgjat maksimumi disa minuta dhe Shopify ju ofron zgjidhjen e plotë për host-im. Ndërkohë, Magento ju ngarkon me përgjegjësinë e shkarkimit, instalimit dhe host-imit të dyqanit të ri.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',364,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:24:\"Hosting the online store\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:325:\"<p>The process of setting up the host in a Shopify store is easy because the whole process can last few minutes, and Shopify provides you the complete solution for hosting your online store. Meanwhile, Magento gives you the responsibility of hosting, downloading, installing and setting up the platform for the new store.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',364,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(377,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,365,1552464983,1544253472,1,0,0,4864,'text','Menaxhimi i përditshëm i dyqanit','','','<p>Të dy, edhe Shopify edhe Magento kanë një seksion të produktit, i cili i mundëson shitësit të menaxhojë artikujt në dyqan. Nëse nuk jeni një specialist i IT ose Web, Shopify është platforma më e lehtë për të menaxhuar dyqanin tuaj online, sepse ka ndërfaqen shumë të thjeshtë.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',365,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:29:\"The everyday Store Management\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:351:\"<p>As soon as you set up your online store, you should add or update product details and manage the inventory. Both Shopify and Magento have a product section which enables the seller to manage to products. If you are not an IT or Web specialist, Shopify is the easiest platform to manage your online store, because of its user-friendly interface.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',365,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(378,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,366,1566577423,1544253472,1,0,0,5120,'textpic','Preferencat e SEO','','','<p>Dyqani më i mirë është ai që ka klientë që blejnë atje. Të dy platformat ofrojnë shikueshmëri të mirë nga vizitorët.E thënë ndryshe, të dyja këto platforma preferohen nga SEO (Search Engine Optimization) i cili rrit numrin e vizitorëve.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',366,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Best for SEO\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:188:\"<p>The best shop is those who have customers shopping there. Both platforms offer good deliver traffic, which is translated as good SEO (search engine optimization) to deliver traffic.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;}',366,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(379,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,367,1552465013,1544253472,1,0,0,5376,'textpic','Stili unik dhe me shije','','','<p>Në të dyja platformat, Shopify dhe Magento, stili e dyqanit krijohet nga të ashtuquajtura Theme. Disa nga Theme bazë ofrohen falas. Theme me stil unik dhe elegant janë kundrejt një çmimi simbolik. Nëse doni një imazh klasik për dyqanin tuaj, Magento ofron më shumë Theme. Nëse doni një imazh të veçantë për dyqanin tuaj, Theme e Shopify janë më elegante nga pikëpamja e dizajnit.</p>\r\n<p>Nga ana teknike, Theme të Shopify janë më të lehta në instalim dhe në modifikim sesa Theme në Magento.</p>\r\n<p>Nga dizajni dhe aspekti UX, Shopify ofron, pa dyshim, Theme më të bukura.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',367,'a:31:{s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Themes for a stylish shop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:589:\"<p>In both platforms, Shopify and Magento, the look and feel of the store are created by themes. Some of their most basic themes are free. Themes with attractive features are in a symbolic price. If you want a classic image of your store, Magento has lots of such themes. If you want a different image of your store, Shopify themes are better from a design view.</p>\r\n<p>From the technical point, Shopify themes are easier in installation and in modification than the Magento themes.</p>\r\n<p>From the design and the UX aspect, Shopify offers the best-looking themes, without any doubt.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',367,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(380,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,368,1566577495,1544253472,1,0,0,5632,'textpic','Pikat e shitjeve','','','<p>Është një zgjidhje e rëndësishme që platforma e shitjeve të ofroje disa variante për pikat e shitjeve.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify ofron një aplikacion të quajtuar \'Point of Sale\', e cila mund të instalohet në çdo pajisje mobile ose desktop, dhe pranon pagesë me kartë krediti.</p>\r\n<p>Magento gjithashtu ofron opsione \'Point of Sale\' të cilat realizohen me Extensions dhe gjithashtu lehtësojnë proçesin e shitjeve.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',368,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"Point Of Sale\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:298:\"<p>It is an important key solution the web platform offers to the point of sale. Shopify offers a Point of Sale app that runs on any mobile or desktop device and accepts credit card payment. Magento also offers Point of Sales options which are extensions in the marketplace.<br /> <br /> &nbsp;</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;}',368,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(381,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,369,1544254526,1544253472,1,0,0,5888,'textpic','Pra, cila është e duhura?','','','<p>Të dyja platformat, Shopify dhe Magento, janë mbizotërueset në e-commerce. Shopify është sistem shumë më i lehtë dhe efektiv. Ndërkohë, Magento është falas në nivel bazë, por është më komplekse për sa i përket instalimeve dhe personalizimit të dyqanit.</p>\r\n<p>Ne nuk mund të përcaktojmë se cila është platforma më e mirë për të gjitha dyqanet online. Ato janë kaq shumë në numër, në nevoja dhe në mënyrën se si shihet si biznes. Por, sugjerimi ynë përmbyllës: hidhini një shikim dyqaneve online në Magento, të krijuar dhe personalizuar nga stafi yne ekspert, si dhe shembuj shumë interesant dyqanesh në Shopify : https://w3development.net/work/.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',369,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"So which one should you choose?\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:562:\"<p>Both Shopify and Magento are powerful e-commerce platforms. Shopify is far easier and fully managed system. Meanwhile, Magento is costless and more complex regarding the installations and customizations.</p>\r\n<p>We cannot define which is the only one choice, to all the stores and business managers that are such differences in needs and in the way they see their business. But as the last suggestion, here are some fantastic Shopify store and some examples of Magento Stores <a href=\"https://w3development.net/work/\"> https://w3development.net/work/</a>.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',369,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(382,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612143778,1544261126,7,0,0,256,'textpic','Specify the terms','','','<p>When someone asks me what I do for the living, I usually answer I am a web designer. This is what people mostly understand, in general.</p>\r\n<p>In fact, this term is used when I am introduced to someone who is not a computer scientist or programmer.</p>\r\n<p>The truth is that people use both <strong>web design</strong> and web development, as the same concept. But, when you apply for a job in the web industry, these terms are completely different.</p>\r\n<p>Let’s specify in details these two terms.<br /> &nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(383,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612144714,1544261398,7,0,0,384,'textpic','Web Design','','','<p>Web design represents the set of technical skills used in building the user interface of the website.<br /> Through the use of color, images, typography, and layout, web design constructs the overall image of the website.</p>\r\n<p>Some different areas of web design include web <em><strong>graphic design</strong></em>, <em><strong>interface design</strong></em>, user <strong><em>experience design</em></strong>, and <em><strong>search engine optimization</strong></em>.</p>\r\n<p>A professional web designer knows the principles of the design and applies them to the web design making it look great and user-friendly.<br /> They make not just a pretty website, but also an easy and attractive interface.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(384,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612144958,1544261453,7,0,0,400,'textpic','Web Development','','','<p>Web development includes front-end development and back-end development. They have a different focus, but many web developers master both skills.</p>\r\n<p>Front-end development focuses on programming the layout of the website. A front-end developer builds the graphical layout of how the user sees the website, by using scripting languages such as <em><strong>HTML</strong></em>, styles of <em><strong>CSS</strong></em>, or <em><strong>JavaScript</strong></em>.</p>\r\n<p>The back-end development requires advanced programming skills to implement the functionalities of the website, such as the interface to a database, connections with web services, and similar features.</p>\r\n<p>A professional web developer masters programming skills such as <strong><em>PHP</em></strong>.</p>\r\n<p>He manages how different APIs (Application Programming Interface) is used to connect different web platforms to make the website more flexible and functional.</p>\r\n<p>In the case when the required functionality is not fulfilled from any current library, a professional back-end developer creates the code from scratch and adds the features that meet the client’s need.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(385,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612145057,1544261509,7,0,0,416,'textpic','Somewhere in between web design and web development','','','<p>Some web developers are specialized in certain areas, but many others can do both web design and web development.</p>\r\n<p>They might prefer working with visual effects of the web, but also implement the layout in the styles of CSS and in tags of HTML.</p>\r\n<p>This kind of web designer is very useful in the industry of web. Similarly, a web developer who owns basic skills of design and visual communication is very helpful in building web projects and in making smart choices while coding.</p>\r\n<p>However, when someone applies for a job in the web technology, or look for someone to work on a website, the position should be well defined: web design or web development.<br /> The advanced skills will make the difference and will lead to the position.</p>\r\n<p>For larger sites and projects, a team of web professionals will cover all the different fields, both web design, and web development.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(386,15,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,1612145184,1544261569,7,0,0,432,'textpic','Full-stack developers','','','<p>Full-stack developers are those who have knowledge of all of the development tasks discussed above.</p>\r\n<p>A full-stack developer should be able to build a website from scratch, beginning with a design, creating the markup of the design, but also implementing back-end functionalities and database queries.</p>\r\n<p>Usually, a full-stack developer has a basic knowledge of design and user experience. Being a full-stack developer does not he should have experience in all programming languages. It’s quite impossible to become an expert or a professional in each programming language.</p>\r\n<p>It’s also hard to learn all the techniques and strategies on how to be most effective in all of the areas we discussed above. Remember, web technologies are evolving every day.</p>\r\n<p>Toward the same goal, both web designers and web developers work for the same goal – to create a website that attracts the users.</p>\r\n<p>To do this, both the design and development must be at the same professional level. A site should be attractive and functional.</p>\r\n<p>The colors, animations and multimedia elements should represent the brand and the interface needs to encourage visitors to stay longer on the website and to use all its functionality.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_clas