 web. Alla fine della configurazione, puoi iniziare a costruire il negozio online.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',359,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"The main differences\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:370:\"<p>Shopify is commercial. You should pay a monthly fee to get its services. Magento is free and open source software. Shopify is hosted by its own host, which makes easier the setup and configurations. Magento is hosted by your hosting. The installation and configuration need web programming skills. At the end of the setup, you can start building the online store.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',359,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(465,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,360,1566578908,1544300427,7,0,0,1280,'textpic','Il sistema più semplice','','','<p>Avviare un negozio online non è per niente facile. Almeno, il sistema deve essere semplice. Quando scegli un sistema che aggiunge stress al tuo lavoro, non potrai concentrarti sui tuoi prodotti e sulle vendite. È meglio costruire il tuo negozio in un sistema che ti mette al agio.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify offre un modo interattivo per costruire il sito web, con una interfaccia molto semplice. Tu puoi impostare il negozio online spostando i componenti della interfaccia.<br /> Gli immagini dei prodotti faranno il tuo negozio unico e interessante. Inoltre, il processo d\'impostazione dei modi di pagamento è così semplice, che tu puoi iniziare subito a fare soldi, senza preoccuparti delle procedure.</p>\r\n<p>L\'inizio con Magento è un po\' diverso. Prima d\'iniziare a vendere in un negozio in Magento, tu dovresti imparare alcuni termini tecnici e del codice. La piattaforma Magento è meno user-friendly e il processo d\'impostazione del negozio richiede più tempo. Magento è un sistema flessibile per venditori esperti in tecnologia, ma un po \'difficile per quelli che non sanno nulla di applicazioni web. Ciò significa che hai bisogno di alcuni trucchi professionali per gestire tutte le funzionalità che offre questo sistema.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',360,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"The easy platform\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1270:\"<p>Starting a new business is not easy. At least, the platform of the web store should be easy and helpful. If you choose a platform that adds stress in your work, then you should not focus on your own products and sales, but in the store itself. You better build your store in a platform you soon master and in which you are comfortable with.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify gives you the interactive way to build the website just by drag and drop the elements in the interface. You can set up the store just by moving the components in the way you like to arrange them, so you can quickly start selling. The process of adding new images to the store makes it unique and personalized. Also, the process of setting up the payment method is so easy so you can soon start making money, without worrying about the procedures.</p>\r\n<p>The beginning with Magento is a bit different. You should learn some technical terms and some code before start selling at a Magento store. Magento platform is less user-friendly and the process of setting up the store requires to navigate is some blocks before becoming a seller. Magento is powerful for experienced users, but a bit difficult for the beginners. This means you need some professional tricks to manage the full functionality it offers.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',360,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(466,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,361,1556605117,1544300427,7,0,0,1536,'textpic','La funzionalità dipende dai Extensions','','','<p>Sia Shopify che Magento hanno un numero enorme di funzioni principali, che includono le attività importanti come marketing, inventario, finanza, ecc. Ma per qualsiasi strumento specifico, tu devi installare una nuova estensione. Tale applicazione software ti aiuta ad aggiungere funzionalità e ad accelerare qualsiasi procedura, così tu puoi concentrarti sulle vendite.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store offre oltre 2 300 applicazioni, gratuite o a pagamento, che tu puoi installarli con un solo click. Alcuni applicazioni utili sono quelli che integrano il tuo negozio con i social media o con l\'email. Questi connessioni aumenteranno notevolmente le vendite del tuo negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace ha oltre 3 000 estensioni, gratuite o a pagamento. Alcuni di essi richiedono delle capacità tecniche per inserirli nel negozio e per personalizzarli.Per i nostri esperti, Magento sembra molto più potente riguardo alla gamma di funzioni extra e nelle estensioni che offre. In pratica, puoi fare tutto con le estensioni Magento. Tutto ciò di cui hai bisogno è scegliere quello giusto e sapere come usarlo correttamente.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',361,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"More Apps means more functions\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1097:\"<p>Both Shopify and Magento have a huge number of main functions, which cover important tasks like marketing, inventory, finance, etc. But for any specific tool, you need to install a new app or an extension of your store. Such software helps you in adding extra functionality and to speed any procedure so you can focus on sales and not on the online store itself.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify App Store offers more than 2 300 applications, free and paid. You can install them by just clicking on it, and personalize it. Some useful apps are those who integrate your store with social media, or with your email. Such connections will increase dramatically the sales of your online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento Marketplace has over 3 000 extensions, free or paid. Some of them require few coding skills to insert them in the online store and to personalize them. But to us, Magento seems powerful in the wide range of extra functions and in the extensions it offers. Practically, you can do quite everything with Magento extensions, and all you need is to choose the right one and to know how to use it properly.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',361,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(467,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,362,1566578952,1544300427,7,0,0,1792,'textpic','Il prezzo è un fattore chiave','','','<p>Durante la scelta della piattaforma web, devi tenere in considerazione il costo economico. Shopify e Magento sono differenti nelle tariffe e nei costi operativi. Il prezzo per ogni mese del Shopify include la tassa dell\'hosting e il costo del servizio di manutenzione. L\'applicazione premium ha un costo aggiuntivo per ogni mese.<br /> Magento è un software gratuito e open source ma non include il costo dell\'hosting. Per molte applicazioni di Magento è necessario consultare uno sviluppatore web per integrarli e configurarli.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',362,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Your budget, a key factor\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:537:\"<p>The budget is a factor you should consider in choosing the web platform. Shopify and Magento differ in their fees and in their operating costs. Shopify comes with a monthly fee, but it includes the host fee and maintenance service fee. Each premium application has an extra monthly fee.</p>\r\n<p>Magento is a free and open source software but it does not include the cost of hosting. Many Magento apps have fees and in an overall overview, you will need to consult to a web developer to integrate and to configure the Magento apps.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',362,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(468,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,363,1564493902,1544300427,7,0,0,2048,'textpic','La dimensione del negozio ti farà decidere','','','<p>Tu puoi fare la scelta tra Shopify oppure Magento, in base alle dimensioni della tua attività.</p>\r\n<p>Shopify offre Shopify Lite che ti consente di vendere tramite Facebook. Shoppify offre inoltre tre pacchetti: Shopify di base, Shopify avanzato e Shopify Plus. Tu puoi sceglierle in base alle tue esigenze e al prezzo. Per una start up migliore, potrai scegliere Advanced Shopify, che contiene un intero set di funzionalità per inizializzare un negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Magento offre il pacchetto Community, un sistema giusto per piccoli negozi e il quello Enterprise per grandi marchi online.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',363,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:42:\"The size of the store will make you decide\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:562:\"<p>You can make the choice between Shopify vs Magento, based on the size of your business. Shopify offers the Shopify Lite which allow you to sell via Facebook. It also offers three packages: Basic Shopify, Advanced Shopify, and Shopify Plus. You can choose them depending on your needs and your budget. For a startup better choose Advanced Shopify. It contains a whole set of features to initialize an online store.</p>\r\n<p>Magento offers the Community package as the right platform for small online shops and the Enterprise package for large online brands.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',363,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(469,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,364,1566579004,1544300427,7,0,0,2304,'textpic','Hosting: come un primo passo','','','<p>Il processo di configurazione dell\'host in un negozio Shopify è molto semplice. L\'intero processo può durare pochi minuti e Shopify ti offre la soluzione completa per l\'hosting del tuo negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Nel frattempo, Magento ti dà la responsabilità di scegliere tu il hosting, e installare il sistema per il nuovo negozio.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',364,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:24:\"Hosting the online store\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:325:\"<p>The process of setting up the host in a Shopify store is easy because the whole process can last few minutes, and Shopify provides you the complete solution for hosting your online store. Meanwhile, Magento gives you the responsibility of hosting, downloading, installing and setting up the platform for the new store.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',364,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(470,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,365,1556605069,1544300427,7,0,0,2560,'textpic','Gli aggiornamenti quotidiani','','','<p>Non appena si imposta il negozio online, è necessario aggiungere i dettagli del prodotto e gestire l\'inventario. Shopify che Magento hanno una sezione speciale che consente al venditore di gestire i prodotti. Se non sei un esperto IT o Web, Shopify è il sistema più semplice per gestire il tuo negozio online, grazie alla sua interfaccia user-friendly.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',365,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:4:\"text\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:29:\"The everyday Store Management\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:351:\"<p>As soon as you set up your online store, you should add or update product details and manage the inventory. Both Shopify and Magento have a product section which enables the seller to manage to products. If you are not an IT or Web specialist, Shopify is the easiest platform to manage your online store, because of its user-friendly interface.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;}',365,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(471,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,366,1566579051,1544300427,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','Il sistema preferito del SEO','','','<p>Il miglior negozio è quello dove i clienti fanno spese. Tutti e due, Magento e Shopify, offrono un ottimo traffico dei clienti, che viene tradotto come un buon SEO (ottimizzazione di motori di ricerca) che aumenta le vendite.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',366,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Best for SEO\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:188:\"<p>The best shop is those who have customers shopping there. Both platforms offer good deliver traffic, which is translated as good SEO (search engine optimization) to deliver traffic.</p>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:10;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;}',366,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(472,19,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,367,1564493961,1544300427,7,0,0,2944,'textpic','Uno stile unico per il negozio','','','<p>In entrambi sistemi, Shopify e Magento, l\'aspetto e lo stile del negozio sono creati da themes. Alcune di queste themes sono gratuiti. Themes con caratteristiche interessanti sono a un prezzo simbolico.</p>\r\n<p>Se tu vuoi un\'immagine classica del tuo negozio, Magento ha molte themes classici. Se desideri un\'immagine diversa del tuo negozio, lo stile di Shopify è migliore da una vista di progettazione.</p>\r\n<p>Dal punto tecnico, themes di Shopify sono più facili nell\'installazione e nella modifica rispetto ai quei di Magento.<br /> Dal design e dall\'aspetto UX, Shopify offre, senza alcun dubbio, uno stile più bello.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',367,'a:31:{s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Themes for a stylish shop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:589:\"<p>In both platforms, Shopify and Magento, the look and feel of the store are created by themes. Some of their most basic themes are free. Themes with attractive features are in a symbolic price. If you want a classic image of your store, Magento has lots of such themes. If you want a different image of your store, Shopify themes are better from a design view.</p>\r\n<p>From the technical point, Shopify themes are easier in installation and in modification than the Magento themes.</p>\r\n<p>From the design and the UX aspect, Shopify offers the best-looking themes, without any doubt.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\