ULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(494,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,415,1564489449,1544303636,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Trende','','','<p>Nëse ndiqni tendencat më të fundit të teknologjisë, do e mendoni vazhdimisht pyetjen se si duket faqja juaj Web ne krahasim me miliona faqe të tjera. Cdo biznes synon rritjen e të ardhurave dhe zhvillimin e identitetit të markës sëtij.</p>\r\n<p>Një faktor kyç në marketing është sigurisht faqja e internetit e kompanisë suaj si dhe sistemi i saj i menaxhimit. Duke pasë parasysh shifrat, sistemi WordPress aktualisht mbizotëron tregun, megjithatë, TYPO3 po merr gjithashtu një rol dominues. Në dilemën mes TYPO3 dhe WordPress, stafi i W3DEVELOPMENT ju ofron një zgjidhje optimale të sistemit CMS, bazuar në kërkesat tuaja.</p>\r\n<p>Duke iu referuar Google Trends, po rendisim karakteristikat kryesore të këtyre dy sistemeve CMS:</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',415,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Trends \";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:704:\"<p>Are you following the new trends and technologies and always asking how is your website compared to millions of others? Everyone is struggling with increasing revenue and developing its brand identity. A key factor in the market is, of course, the website of your company, and its content management system. Tracing the run of website market, WordPress has already been in the foreground, however, TYPO3 is also taking respectful place currently. In the competition TYPO3 vs WordPress, our team tries to offer an optimal solution for our clients by choosing the CMS according to their requirements.<br /> <br /> Referring to Google Trends, below are listed the key characteristics of both the CMS:</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',415,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(495,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,416,1556603549,1544303636,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Versioni i Parë','','','<p>Në vitin 1997, Kasper Skårhøj zhvilloi nga fillimi produktin më të ri TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Në vitin 2003, Matt Mullenweg njoftoi që versioni i parë i WordPress është në dispozicion të përdoruesve.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',416,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"First Version\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:168:\"<p>TYPO3’s development was started from scratch by Kasper Skårhøj in 1997. In 2003, Matt Mullenweg announced the availability of the first version of WordPress.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',416,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(496,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,417,1556603557,1544303636,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Tendencë dhe aktualitet','','','<p>Në të vërtetë, TYPO3 është CMS i përdorur nga 130.998 faqe interneti. Ky sistem është falas. Ndërkohë, WordPress është CMS i përdorur nga 27,449,706 faqe interneti. Ky sistem është gjithashtu falas dhe shumë e njohur për ndërtimin e faqeve personale.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',417,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:19:\"Trend and actuality\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:228:\"<p>Actually, TYPO3 is the CMS used by 130,998 websites. It is free to use. Meanwhile, WordPress is the CMS used by 27,449,706 websites. It is also free to use, and it is well known as a semantic personal publishing platform.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',417,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(497,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,418,1556603567,1544303636,7,0,0,4096,'textpic','Thjeshtësia','','','<p>TYPO3 ofron një ndërfaqe të lehtë për menaxhimin e faqes web. Përdoruesi thjesht do të vendosë menunë, përmbajtjen dhe përmbajtjen e faqes web. WordPress e tregon thjeshtësinë nga vetë emri i tij. Është shumë i thjeshtë në përdorim dhe çdo blogg-er e dashuron. Ju nuk keni nevojë të dini ndonjë truk teknologjik për të shtuar përmbajtje në faqen tuaj te internetit në WordPress.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',418,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Simplicity\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:322:\"<p>TYPO3 offers an easy implementation of content management. The user will just drag and drop the menu, content, and pages in the dashboard. WordPress shows the simplicity in its own name. It is user-friendly and each blogger loves it. You don’t need to master any technological tool to add content in your website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',418,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(498,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,419,1556603587,1544303636,7,0,0,4352,'textpic','Ndërfaqe Responsive Web','','','<p>TYPO3 ofron mundësinë e krijimit të ndërfaqes Responsive Web, duke përdorë të ashtu-quajturat TYPO3 Template, pjesë e funksionalitetit bazë të TYPO3. Funksionalitete shtesë mund të modifikohen duke përdorë TYPO3 Extensions. Ky CMS ofron mundësi pafund për ndërtimin e një faqe interneti plotësisht të personalizuar. WordPress ndërton funksionalitetin e faqes web duke përdorur WordPress Extensions. Ndërkohë, dizajni i faqes në WordPress stilohet nga WordPress Theme e përzgjedhur.</p>\r\n<p>Nuk ekziston një pavarësi e plotë midis Extensions dhe Theme në WordPress. Kjo do të thotë që funksionalitete të caktuara janë në varësi të stilit të ndërfaqes.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',419,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Responsive Layout\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:595:\"<p>TYPO3 builds a responsive layout upon TYPO3 templates, which are core independent. Extra functionality could be added by using the TYPO3 extension. This CMS offers unlimited possibilities for building a fully optional website. WordPress builds the functionality by using WordPress Extensions.<br /> <br /> Meanwhile, the design of the website in WordPress is the style of a WordPress theme. But there does not exist a full independence between the extensions used by the developer and the WordPress Theme chosen by the designer. Certain features are dependent on and related to the theme.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',419,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(499,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,420,1556603608,1544303636,7,0,0,4608,'textpic','Qëllimi i faqes Web','','','<p>TYPO3 është shumë i përshtatshëm për faqet e internetit të mëdha, sisteme web për kompani apo biznese. Ndërkohë, WordPress është sistem për cdo faqe të thjeshtë, që është në fillimet e saj. WordPress përdoret shumë në bloget personale, faqet e internetit të thjeshta, apo faqet e internetit për biznese të vogla.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',420,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:26:\"The purpose of the website\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:261:\"<p>TYPO3 is very suitable for large websites used for companies or businesses. Meanwhile, WordPress is the CMS used in the very beginning of any website, for different purposes. WordPress is very used in personal blogs, small websites, or business websites.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',420,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(500,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,421,1556603618,1544303636,7,0,0,4864,'textpic','Siguria','','','<p>TYPO3 ofron një sërë funksionesh të integruara për sigurinë e të dhënave në Web. WordPress ofron siguri optimale kur sistemi azhornohet rregullisht.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',421,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:8:\"Security\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:145:\"<p>TYPO3 offers a set of built-in features for security. WordPress provides its optimal security when the system is updated on regular basis.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',421,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(501,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,422,1556603627,1544303636,7,0,0,5120,'textpic','Struktura','','','<p>TYPO3 i organizon faqet në një strukturë hierarkike, të ngjashme me sistemin e dosjeve dhe skedarëve. WordPress i liston të gjitha faqet njëra nën tjetrën.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',422,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:16:\"Layout structure\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:140:\"<p>TYPO3 organizes the pages in a tree-structure, similar to the folders in a filesystem. WordPress lists all pages one under the other.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',422,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(502,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,423,1564489484,1544303636,7,0,0,5376,'textpic','Cili është më i miri, TYPO3 apo WordPress?','','','<p>Për shumë arsye, nuk ka një konkurrencë të drejtpërdrejtë mes TYPO3 dhe WordPress. Ato ndryshojnë në natyrën dhe qëllimin e faqes Web, dhe të dy këto sisteme udhëheqin fushat përkatëse.</p>\r\n<p>Ju sugjerojmë të zgjidhni WordPress nëse:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit është relativisht e thjeshtë, me disa karakteristika bazë.</li> 	<li>Ju keni një buxhet të vogël ose të mesëm dhe preferoni të menaxhoni vetë faqen e internetit.</li> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit nuk ka pse të jetë në gjuhë të ndryshme.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>TYPO3 është CMS i duhur nëse:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit është e organizuar në një strukturë komplekse me faqe dhe nën-faqe.</li> 	<li>Faqja juaj e internetit do të jetë promovimi i biznesit tuaj, në një audiencë ndërkombëtare, dhe në shumë gjuhë.</li> 	<li>Faqja do përmbajë të dhëna të integruara nga burime të tjera.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Ju keni një buxhet të mesëm për të shpenzuar për faqen tuaj, në fazën e projektimit, ndërtimit dhe mirëmbajtjes.<br /> W3DEVELOPMENT është një grup ekspertësh web, të profilizuar në fushën e aplikacioneve web për biznese.</p>\r\n<p>Ju garantojmë se do jeni në rrugën e duhur për të pasur sukses në biznesin tuaj.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',423,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"the best CMS\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1104:\"<p>Which one is the best, TYPO3 or WordPress?</p>\r\n<p>For many reasons, there is no direct competition between TYPO3 and WordPress. They differ in the types of the websites they suite, and both of them lead the respective fields.<br /> <br /> You better choose WordPress if :</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Your website is relatively simple, with some basic features.</li> 	<li>You have a small or a medium budget, and you prefer to manage yourself the website.</li> 	<li>Your website does not need to be in multiple languages.</li> </ul>\r\n<p><br /> TYPO3 is the right CMS if:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Your website is organized in a complex structure of pages and sub-pages.</li> 	<li>Your website will be the promotion of your business in many languages.</li> 	<li>There should be data integrated from other sources.</li> 	<li>You have a medium to large budget to spend on your website for assistance with the design, build and maintenance.</li> </ul>\r\n<p><br /> <br /> W3DEVELOPMENT do have expertise web developers with business excellence, so we can guarantee you will be guided to right track to succeed in your business.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:300;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:1;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',423,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(503,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,427,1564488864,1544307259,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','5 modelet më të njohura të dizajnit Responsive Web','','','<p>Gjithnjë e më shumë përdorues kërkojnë në web duke përdorur pajisje të llojeve të ndryshme. Ato ndryshojnë në madhësi, duke nisur nga ekrani në laptop madhesinë e ekranit të Smartphone. Projektimi i faqes Web bëhet i vështirë, sepse duhen pasë parasysh të gjitha këto lloje të ndryshme ekranesh.</p>\r\n<p>Faqet Responsive Web janë të ndërtuara në mënyrë të tillë që dizajni të përshtatet me madhësinë e ekranit. Por, ndërtimi i një faqeje Responsive Web nuk është aspak i lehtë, sepse çdo ditë rritet numri i paisjeve të reja Smartphone. Modelet e dizajnit Responsive Web janë bashkësi rregullash që duhen ndjekur gjatë procesit të zhvillimit të faqes Web. Ato përfshijnë disa komponente të përsëritur që ndërtojnë strukturën e ndërfaqes Web.</p>\r\n<p>Projektimi i ndërfaqes Web përfshin përcaktimin e disa parametrave teknikë të tillë si gjerësia, lartësia, madhësia e shkrimit dhe e imazheve. Ekspertë të grafikës sugjerojnë këto pesë modele të dizajnit Web, si një zgjidhje e mirë për projektimin e ndërfaqes:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Mostly Fluid,</li> 	<li>Column Drop,</li> 	<li>Layout Shifter,</li> 	<li>Tiny Tweaks,</li> 	<li>Off Canvas.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Le të përshkruajmë më në detaje secilin prej këtyre modeleve.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',427,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:44:\"5 Examples of Responsive Web Design Patterns\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1312:\"<p>5 Examples of Responsive Web Design Patterns<br /> Nowadays, more and more users browse the web using different devices, in different screens. They vary in size, from desktop screen to tablet and Smartphone screen. The web development becomes difficult, assuming all these different options in size. By following some web design patterns, the workflow is kept more manageable. Building a responsive website isn’t easy at all while developing for multiple devices.<br /> <br /> Responsive web design patterns are considered as rules to follow or kind of inspiration during the web development process. A responsive web design makes the site adjusts the layout to different sizes of the screen. If we focus on the modules and components of the layout, you will follow some patterns. They are some repeated components that build the design system. Web design patterns technically implement measures such as width, height, font size, and resolution.<br /> <br /> Professional designers suggest these five web design patterns as a good solution for web design project. These web design patterns are:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Mostly Fluid,</li> 	<li>Column Drop,</li> 	<li>Layout Shifter,</li> 	<li>Tiny Tweaks,</li> 	<li>Off Canvas.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Each of these web design patterns is explained in details, as follows.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',427,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(504,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,428,1569922845,1544307259,7,0,0,3072,'textpic','Modeli Mostly Fluid','','','<p>Modeli Mostly Fluid është gjërësisht i përdorur, për faktin se është i thjeshtë për t\'u implementuar. Ai përmban kolona të ndryshme me margjina më të mëdha për ndërfaqe më të madhe. Ky model web design sugjerohet për revista apo për faqe Web të lajmeve të modës.</p>\r\n<p>Modeli Mostly Fluid përfshin funksionalitetet e një menuje zbritëse, lidhje me rrjetet sociale etj. Në këtë model të dizajnimit Web, faqja ndryshon kufijtë sipas madhësisë së ekranit të pajisjes. Në smartphone, ndërfaqja rregullon gjerësitë e kolonave.</p>\r\n<p>Avantazhi i kësaj strukture është se faqosja ndryshon vetëm kur ngushtohet gjerësia e ekranit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,1,1,NULL,'',0,'',428,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:31:\"Mostly Fluid Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:641:\"<p>The very popular web design pattern is mostly fluid. One of the reasons for its popularity is the fact it is simple to implement.It contains different columns with larger margins on the larger interface. This web design pattern is suggested for magazines or fashion news websites. It can include functionalities of a drop-down menu, social accounts links, etc. In this web design pattern, the layout changes the margins according to the screen size of the device. On Smartphone, the layout reflows and arranges the columns vertically. The advantage of this structure is that the layout changes only when a smaller screen width occurs.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',428,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(505,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,429,1569922867,1544307259,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Moduli Drop Column','','','<p>Ky model përmban kolona të ndryshme, por ndërsa ekrani ngushtohet, numri i kolonave zvogëlohet. Ky model i dizenjimit web tenton të mbushë të gjitha hapsirat e mundëshme.</p>\r\n<p>Drop Column është i përkryer për faqet Responsive Web ku përdoruesi do të lexojë nga e gjithë gjerësia e ekranit. Madhësitë e segmenteve kanë tendencën të mos ndryshojnë. Ndëfaqja është e ndërtuar në segmente të ndryshme për rezolucione të ndryshme të ekranit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',429,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Column Drop Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:413:\"<p>This pattern contains different columns but while the screen narrows, the columns are reduced. This web design pattern tends to fill the available viewpoint. It is perfect for responsive websites that users will see from the wide range of screen sizes.The sizes of segments tent to stay the same. The layout is built in different breakpoint for different screen resolutions, and it differs for each design.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',429,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(506,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,430,1569922913,1544307259,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Modeli Layout Shifter','','','<p>Modeli Layout Shifter është shumë kompleks, sepse ndryshon strukturën për secilën gjerësi ekrani. Kjo gjë krijon vështirësi gjatë fazës së implementimit. Për këtë arsye, ky model nuk përdoret gjërësisht.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',430,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:33:\"Layout Shifter Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:278:\"<p>The layout shifter pattern does the most to adapt to the different displays sizes. The pattern is complex because it changes for each breakpoint for different widths. This requires more effort during the implementation phase, and this makes the patterns not much popular.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',430,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(507,16,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,431,1569927684,1544307259,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Modeli Tiny Tweaks','','','<p>Ky model bën përshtatjen duke ndryshuar madhësinë e shkronjave ose madhësinë e imazheve. Faqet Web që ndjekin këtë model ndryshojnë madhësinë e shkronjave sipas gjerësisë së ekranit ku përdoruesi shfleton Web. Nëse përdoruesi po e lexon nga një ekran desktop, ai do të shohë faqen me shkrim dhe me imazhe më të mëdha.</p>\r\n<p>Ky model i dizajnit të Web përdoret kryesisht në paraqitjen me një kolonë të vetme, të cilat mund të përmbajnë artikuj të gjatë.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',431,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Tiny tweaks Web Design Pattern\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:411:\"<p>This pattern makes the adjustments by changing the font sizes, or resizing the images or moving the content. Websites that follow this pattern will change font size according to the width of the Users that browse the website from a desktop screen will see the site with bigger fonts and bigger images. This web design pattern is mostly applied in single column layouts, which might contain long articles.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',431,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(508,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,435,1564488269,1544307653,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Ja pse biznesi juaj duhet të ketë një faqe interneti.','','','<p>Cdo ditë e më tepër rritet numri i njerëzve që përdorin internetin. Për cdo informacion që iu nevojitet, ata do e kërkojnë në internet. Me zhvillimin e teknologjisë dhe internetit, ju duhet t\'i shikoni të gjithë si klientë potencial.</p>\r\n<p>Të rinjtë sot kërkojnë në internet edhe për gjërat që blejnë ose shërbimet që u nevojiten. Prandaj është krejt e natyrshme që konsumatorët të mendojnë se çdo biznes është i pranishëm në ueb, në faqen e vet të internetit.</p>\r\n<p>Të qenit aktiv në mediat sociale është njëra anë. Gjithashtu, duhet një faqe interneti ku ndjekësit mund të blejnë produktin tuaj ose mund të kërkojnë më shumë detaje për shërbimet tuaja.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',435,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Advantages of having a website\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:605:\"<p>The number of people that are using the internet is increasing each day. If they need information, they will search it on the Internet.<br /> In this technologic era, you should see all of them as potential customers, as they will search on the web even for the things they buy or services they need.<br /> Having a website is so normal that customers suppose every business is present on the web on its own website.<br /> <br /> Being active in the social media is one side, but you also need a website where the followers can purchase your product or can search for more details of your services.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',435,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(509,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,436,1566217367,1544307653,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Një faqe interneti rrit ndërgjegjësimin për produktet dhe shërbimet tuaja.','','','<p>Faqja e internetit e biznesit tuaj është mënyra më e lehtë që klientët të kenë qasje në produktet ose shërbimet që ju ofroni. Këto produkte është mirë t\'i vendosni në faqen kryesore, në mënyrë që blerësit ti shohin sa më shpejt që të jetë e mundur.</p>\r\n<p>Faqja e internetit duhet të paraqesë listën e plotë të produkteve që ofron biznesi juaj. Kjo listë tërheq klientin, i cili fillon kërkimin e një produkti, madje blen edhe një të dytë. Ndoshta ai nuk e dinte se biznesi juaj e shet këtë produkt, dhe prandaj duhet afishimi i një liste të plotë të artikujve në faqen e internetit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',436,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:62:\"A website increases awareness about your products and services\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:486:\"<p>The website of your business is the easiest way the customers access the products or services you offer. You better put them on the homepage, so they access it as soon as possible. The website should better present the full list of the products that your business. This list attracts the customer which starts searching a product and buys a second one. Maybe he didn’t know your business sells it too, and that’s the importance of showing a full list of items on the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',436,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(510,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,437,1564488394,1544307653,7,0,0,4096,'textpic','Një faqe interneti punon pavarësisht orarit tuaj.','','','<p>Faqja Ueb e biznesit tuaj do të jetë online 24 orë në ditë, 365 ditë në vit, duke iu dhënë informacion miliona njerëzve çdo ditë. Gjithashtu, ajo do bëjë të mundur që klientët tuaj t\'ju kontaktojnë jashtë orarit tuaj të punës, nëpërmjet porosive ose email.</p>\r\n<p>Faqja juaj e internetit, e projektuar nga W3DEVELOPMENT, punon për ju, ndërsa jeni në kohën tuaj të lirë ose në gjumë.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',437,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:43:\"A website increases your hours of operation\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:341:\"<p>Not only will your website be there 24 hours a day, 365 days a year with the possibility of reaching millions of people every day, but it will make it possible for your customers to contact you outside of your normal business hours. Your website, designed by W3DEVELOPMENT, is still working for you while you are at leisure or asleep.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',437,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(511,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,438,1566217414,1544307653,7,0,0,4352,'textpic','Një faqe interneti redukton shpenzimet e biznesit tuaj.','','','<p><em>Një faqe interneti zvogëlon koston e publikimit:</em> Është media me koston më të ulët, ku mund të reklamoni biznesin tuaj dhe produktet e tij. Në këtë mënyrë, ju do të reduktoni letrat dhe materialet e printuara. Hapësira Ueb nuk është një promocion lokal, por një reklamë ndërkombëtare.</p>\r\n<p><em>Një faqe interneti zvogëlon koston e marketingut:</em> Ju shpenzoni shumë orë në zgjedhjen e fjalës së duhur për ta shkruar në një hapësirë të vogël në një reklamë gazete, ose në 30 sekonda në TV. Një faqe interneti ofron një hapësirë të pakufizuar për biznesin tuaj. Ju mund të vendosni sa më shumë informacion, duke shtuar të gjitha mjetet multimediale dhe duke e bërë atë më tërheqëse se çdo media tjetër.</p>\r\n<p><em>Një faqe interneti zvogëlon shpenzimet e komunikimit:</em> ajo përmban të gjithë informacionin që blerësit duan të dinë, duke përfshirë imazhet e produkteve, hartën e dyqaneve tuaja, stafin që ofron shërbimet, numrin e telefonit dhe e-mail ku mund t\'ju shkruajnë, si dhe çdo informacion që ju dëshironi të ndani me klientët tuaj. Partnerët e biznesit, stafi juaj, furnitorët, si dhe të gjithë të interesuarit për produktet dhe shërbimet tuaja, do të marrin informacionin e plotë nga faqja juaj në internet.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',438,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:23:\"A website reduces costs\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1214:\"<p>A good website reduces publishing cost: It is the most affordable media where you can advertise your business and its products. You will reduce papers and print materials, and it is never locally, but a worldwide advertisement. You can keep your website more current, more affordable and easier to manage than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces marketing cost: You spend plenty hours in choosing the right word to say in a small space of a newspaper ad, or in a half minute in TV. A website offers an unlimited space for your business, you can put as many information as you need, by adding all type of multimedia content and making it more attractive than any other media.</p>\r\n<p>A good website reduces communication costs: The potential customers will get in the website all the information they need about your business, the images of the products, the map of the stores, the members of the team that offer the services, the phone number and e-mail where they can reach you, and any information you wish to communicate to the customers, but not only. Business partners, your team, suppliers, and everyone interested in your products and services will get this information from your website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',438,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(512,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,439,1564488729,1544307653,7,0,0,4608,'textpic','Një faqe interneti rrit imazhin e kompanisë tuaj.','','','<p>Faqja e internetit është një përfaqësim i vizionit të biznesit tuaj. Ajo duhet të pasqyrojë imazhin e kompanisë suaj.</p>\r\n<p>Një faqe Ueb elegante dhe e projektuar nga W3DEVELOPMENT, do të nxjerrë në pah vlerat më të mira të dyqanit tuaj. Ajo duhet të jetë moderne, e azhurnuar, madje edhe nëse është një biznes i vogël, faqja e internetit do të portretizojë biznesin tuaj në më të mirën e mundëshme.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',439,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:37:\"A website enhances your company image\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:429:\"<p>The website is a representation of the vision of your business. It should reflect the spirit of you and your company. If it’s stylish and designed by W3DEVELOPMENT, it will highlight the best values for your store and products. It should be modern and updated, and even if it is a small business, it will portray itself in its big stature. The way you build your website is the image that the customers will perceive it.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',439,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(513,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,440,1566217461,1544307653,7,0,0,4864,'textpic','Një faqe interneti mund të përmirësojë shërbimin ndaj klientit.','','','<p>Një faqe interneti është një mënyrë e shkëlqyer për të tërhequr klientët tuaj. Ajo është gjithashtu një mënyrë shumë e mirë për t\'i rikthyer ata të vijnë tek ju sa herë që kanë nevojë për produktet ose shërbimet tuaja. Përveç informacionit që lidhet direkt me produktin, ju mund të ofroni ndonjë sugjerim se si të kujdesen për produktin që kanë blerë tek ju, ose si t\'i kombinojnë këto produkte me sende të tjera.</p>\r\n<p>Nëse biznesi juaj ofron një shërbim, mund të shtoni në faqen tuaj një tutorial se si ta përdorin këtë shërbim.</p>\r\n<p>Një tjetër faqe interesante e hapsirës tuaj në Ueb mund të jetë zona FAQ, ku klientët gjejnë përgjigje të shumë pyetjeve në lidhje me shërbimet e biznesit tuaj.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',440,'a:31:{s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:38:\"A website can improve customer service\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:601:\"<p>A website is a great way to attract your customers but is also a great way to keep them coming back to you whenever they need again your products or services. Besides the information related directly to the product, you can offer any suggestions how to care about the product they’ve purchased from you, or how to combine to other items. If your business offers a service, you can add in your website any post or tutorial how to use this service. Another interesting page of your website might be an FAQ page, where the customers find any the answers related to the services of your business.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";}',440,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(514,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,441,1566217871,1544307653,7,0,0,5120,'textpic','Një faqe interneti krijon mundësi për komunikim me stafin, bashkëpunëtorët, agjentët dhe furnitorët.','','','<p>Ju mund të organizoni përmbajtjen e faqes në nivele të ndryshme. Përdorues të ndryshëm mund të lexojnë informacione që kanë lidhje me to.</p>\r\n<p>Për shembull, ju mund të postoni informacion për ekipin tuaj në një hapsirë Ueb të mbyllur, të cilën ata arrijnë vetëm me fjalëkalimin e duhur. Këto informacione të brendshme mund jenë në lidhje me ndryshimet në staf, orare apo detyra për stafin, ngjarje ose njoftime të ndryshme, etj. Ndërkohë, përdoruesit të internetit kanë qasje vetëm në detajet e produktit, format e kontaktit dhe postimet publike që lidhen me kompaninë tuaj.</p>\r\n<p>Ju mund të vendosni shumë ose pak informacion, sa të doni në faqen tuaj.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',441,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:90:\"A website opens new channels of communication with staff, affiliates, agents and suppliers\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:500:\"<p>You can organize the content of the website in different levels, so different users can read vary information related to them. You can post information for your team in a closed location, so they reach it only by a password. It might include changes in the team, task schedule, events or notifications. Meanwhile, the wide web users access the product details, contact forms and public posts related to your company. You can put as much or as little information as you want on your site.&nbsp;</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',441,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(515,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,442,1564436156,1544307653,7,0,1,5376,'textpic','Na kontaktoni','','','<p>Cfare po prisni? Na kontaktoni sot, dhe le të flasim për faqen tuaj!</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',1,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',442,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:87:\"<p>What are you waiting for? Contact us today, and let’s talk about your website!</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',442,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(516,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,353,1613898959,1544307817,1,0,1,2240,'theme_blogteaser','[Translate to Italian:] Responsive Web Design','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125901,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Responsive Web Design</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Responsive Design is the technique which allows the website to adapt to the device of the user. The programmer can write the code once and publish it everywhere, meaning less work for him. The number of visitors that come to the website from a smartphone, tablet or iPods is increasing every minute. Statistically, in 2018 there are about 2.6 billion people in the world using the smartphone. Actually, the small businesses are increasing their presence in the mobile applications, using their websites, the social media, and other applications which promote their business. This means more and more websites are going to be Responsive.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=23</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">34</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',353,'a:23:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";i:125901;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:11:\"pi_flexform\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',353,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(517,6,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,352,1613898963,1544307817,1,0,0,2072,'theme_blogteaser','Shopify verso Magento','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,125902,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify vs Magento</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Recentemente, il mercato delle piattaforme di e-commerce ha un solo nome: Magento. Un modo diverso di creare un negozio online sta attirando i venditori che i clienti, e si chiama Shopify.\n\nShopify e Magento sono due delle piattaforme più popolari nella categoria e-commerce. In questo articolo si mettono in luce le differenze tra queste due piattaforme, cosi tu puoi decidere qual è la giusta piattaforma di e-commerce per il tuo negozio online.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=19</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">31</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>','',0,'',352,'a:24:{s:5:\"CType\";s:16:\"theme_blogteaser\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:125902;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"pi_flexform\";s:1065:\"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" standalone=\"yes\" ?>\n<T3FlexForms>\n    <data>\n        <sheet index=\"options\">\n            <language index=\"lDEF\">\n                <field index=\"headline\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify vs Magento</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"content\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">Shopify and Magento are two of the most popular e-commerce platforms on the market. They differ a lot from each other. In this article, these differences are highlighted, so you can decide which is the right e-commerce platform for your online store.</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"link\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">t3://page?uid=19</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"image\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\">31</value>\n                </field>\n                <field index=\"alt\">\n                    <value index=\"vDEF\"></value>\n                </field>\n            </language>\n        </sheet>\n    </data>\n</T3FlexForms>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',352,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(518,13,0,0,0,0,0,1581950621,0,518,1580816373,1580816373,13,0,0,3072,'textpic','A website moves you a step forward from your competitors','','','<p>If your customers can’t find your business online, they will find your competitors. If you aren’t present on the web, you are losing many opportunities.&nbsp;It is important that website of your store to be well designed, easy to navigate, and full of information and product details of your business or your customers won’t buy anything. You should see it as an online representation of your shop and business. If the website is ugly or incomplete, it will send the clients to another company. It often happens that a customer chooses to buy a product online just because it is described in details and the website looks good and is stylish. So, you must have a professional-looking site if you want to be taken seriously. Studies show that once a consumer has an idea of what they need or want, they start researching, and 72% of them go online to find the service they need, according to this&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.pardot.com/buyer-journey/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">report</a></p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(519,13,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,518,1564488342,1544308611,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Me një faqe interneti, ju jeni një hap përpara konkurrentëve tuaj.','','','<p>Nëse blerësit nuk mund ta gjejnë biznesin tuaj online, ata do të gjejnë konkurrentët tuaj. Nëse nuk jeni të pranishëm në internet, ju humbni shumë mundësi.</p>\r\n<p>Është e rëndësishme që faqja e internetit të jetë e projektuar mirë, e lehtë për të lundruar, si dhe me informacion të plotë dhe të detajuar në lidhje produktet e biznesit tuaj. Ju duhet ta shihni faqen Ueb si një prezantim online të dyqanit dhe biznesit tuaj.</p>\r\n<p>Nëse faqja e internetit është e shëmtuar ose jo e plotë, ajo do t\'i largojë klientët drejt një kompanie tjetër. Shpesh ndodh që një klient zgjedh për të blerë një produkt online vetëm se produkti përshkruhet në detaje dhe faqja e internetit duket këndshëm. Imazhi i biznesit tuaj përfaqësohet nga cilësia e faqes së internetit.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',518,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:56:\"A website moves you a step forward from your competitors\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:670:\"<p>If your customers can’t find your business online, they will find your competitors. If you aren’t present on the web, you are losing many opportunities. It is important that website is well designed and easy to navigate, and full of information and product details of your business. You should see it as an online representation of your shop and business. If the website is ugly or incomplete, it will send the clients to another company. It often happens that a customer chooses to buy a product online just because it is described in details and the website looks good and is stylish. The image of your business is represented by the quality of its website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',518,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(520,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,443,1564487063,1544308966,7,0,0,3328,'textpic','Trendet Mobile web','','','<p>Ekspertët e dizajn në web përballen me sfidat teknike por edhe vazhdojnë të krijojnë faqe të thjeshta për përdoruesin, elegante dhe të përshtatshme me çdo pajisje mobile.Në vitin 2017 ka avancuar shumë përdorimi i faqeve të internetit në paisjet mobile.</p>\r\n<p>Aktualisht, lundrimi në aplikacione web mobile numëron më shumë përdorues sesa lundrimi në web nga kompjuter apo laptop. Kjo është një nga arsyet pse viti 2018 do të sjellë funksionalitete dhe mënyra të reja për paisjet mobile.</p>\r\n<p>Në vazhdim përmenden disa tendenca të dizajnit web për vitin 2018.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',443,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Mobile web trends\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:512:\"<p>Web designers deal with the technical challenges that are large in number, and still continue to create user-friendly sites, stylish and flexible with every device and just beautiful all at once. 2017 made more advancement in mobile browsing, who now counts more users than desktop browsing. This is a reason why 2018 is going to have fully mobile functionalities in new ways. Meanwhile, desktops will evolve in such way to stay relevant.</p>\r\n<p>So, let’s take a look at some web design trends in 2018.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',443,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(521,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,444,1566224128,1544308966,7,0,0,3584,'textpic','Dritë-hijet','','','<p>Dritë-hijet janë një teknikë e herëshme grafike, por sapo është cilësuar si trend i dizajnit web për vitin 2018. Kjo teknikë thekson rëndësinë e dizejnimit web në një hapësirë tre-dimensionale. Në listën e tendencave të dizajnit web për vitin 2018, do të vini re animacione, ilustrime dhe shkrime të mëdha. Të gjitha këto efekte grafike ndryshojnë shumë nga efektet e zvogëluara, një tendencë kjo e viteve të fundit.</p>\r\n<p>Koncepti i thellësisë në grafik i jep faqes së internetit një ndjenjë unike dhe një përshtypje të paharrueshme. Ai krijon ndjenjën e një imazhi të vërtetë, ndonjëse është abstrakt. Ky efekt mund të aplikohet në sfondin e faqes web, në logon ose ndonjë imazh grafik të ndërfaqes. Efekti i thellësisë në një faqe web 2D shpesh bëhet një mënyrë e mirë për të theksuar një komponent në dizajn. E gjithë ndërfaqja grafike merr më shumë vëmendje kur përdoret një perspektivë e thellësisë.</p>\r\n<p>Në këtë shembull, duke shtuar dritë-hije, krijohet efekti i thellësisë dhe një perspektivë mbresëlënëse nga lart-poshtë.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',444,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:22:\"Drop shadows and depth\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:998:\"<p>Drop shadows are an old graphical technique, but it’s the newly implemented as web design trend in 2018, and it highlights the importance of designing the web in a three-dimensional space. In the list of web design trends 2018, you will notice broken grids, animations, illustrations and big fonts. All these graphical effects differ a lot from the minimalism which was a trend during past years.</p>\r\n<p>The concept of the depth in the graphic gives to the website the unique feeling and a memorable impression. It creates the sense of a real image, even if it is an abstract one. This effect is a web design trend in 2018 applied in web background, logo or any other graphical representation. The effect of depth in a flat page can be also a powerful tool to emphasize an element in the design. The whole design will get more attention when used this depth perspective.</p>\r\n<p>In this example, playing with translucency adds depth effect, and creates an impressive top-down perspective.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',444,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(522,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,445,1566224189,1544308966,7,0,0,3840,'textpic','Sfonde me ngjyra të forta','','','<p>Tendencat e dizajnit të web për vitin 2018 janë absolutisht plot me ngjyra ndezura dhe plot dritë. Në vitet e fundit, markat e njohura përdorën më shumë \"ngjyra të sigurta\", që do të thotë nuk eksperimentuan shumë me ngjyra të forta. Për këtë vit, ekspertët e dizajn në web po marrin guximin në përdorimin e ngjyrave, duke përfshirë nuanca më të ndricuara. Përveç ngjyrave, titujt në web nuk janë më vetëm horizontale, por janë të ridimensionuar me tituj në kënde të ndryshme.</p>\r\n<p>Ngjyra të gjalla sugjerohen sidomos për markat e reja sepse ato tërheqin menjëherë vëmendjen e përdoruesve. Ky trend mund të jetë i duhuri për çdo markë që dëshiron të largohet nga dizajni i tyre tradicional. Efekti i ngjyrave të ndezura është tërheqja e vëmendjes, sidomos kur aplikohet në butona, links apo njoftime.</p>\r\n<p>Në këtë shembull, është zgjedhur një ngjyrë e kuqe e mrekullueshme dhe e përzier dhe nuancat e blu-marinës. Vendi duket shumë profesional dhe aspak i mërzitshëm apo i zymtë.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',445,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:35:\"Vibrant and saturated color schemes\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:932:\"<p>Web design trends 2018 are absolutely full of super excess colors online. In the past years, brands and designers used more the “web-safe colors”. In this year, web designers are becoming more courageous in their approach to color—including super-saturation and vibrant shades. Apart the colors, web headers are no longer just horizontal but resized with slashes and hard angles.</p>\r\n<p>Vibrant colors as web design trends in 2018 are suggested to the new brands because they attract immediately the attention of the users. This trend can be also perfect for every brand who wants to distant their design from the traditional one.</p>\r\n<p>The effect of saturated colors is the attraction of the attention, especially when used in buttons, links, alerts, and notifications. In this example, is chosen a striking red color and mixed with blues and navy tones. The site looks very professional, not dull or boring at all.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',445,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(523,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,446,1566224251,1544308966,7,0,0,4096,'textpic','Sfonde me grimca','','','<p>Një nga tendencat e dizajnit web për vitin 2018 është sfondi që përmban grimca, forma të thjeshta gjeometrike, imazhe komplekse apo animacione. Efektet mund të jenë rrathë, shumë trekëndësha të thjeshtë ose forma të tjera gjeometrike.</p>\r\n<p>Dizajni përfshin një skenë dinamike, ku këto grimca lëvizin rreth diçkaje, dridhen, kërcejnë ose reagojnë ndaj veprimeve të përdoruesit. Roli kryesor i këtij sfondi është që t\'i japë ndërfaqes një lëvizje dhe një efekt gjeometrik.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',446,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"Particle backgrounds\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:483:\"<p>One of the web design trends 2018 is the backgrounds containing simple dots, simple geometric shapes, complex images and particles animations. The effects might be vibrant balls, few circles, and a lot of plain triangles or other geometric shapes. The design includes a dynamic scene, when these particles move around something, vibrate, dance, or react to the user’s actions.</p>\r\n<p>The main role of all this scenery is to give the interface a motion and a geometric vibe.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',446,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(524,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,447,1566224306,1544308966,7,0,0,4352,'textpic','Në prioritet grafika për aplikacionet mobile','','','<p>Ndërsa numri i përdoruesve të paisjeve mobile është në rritje, përdorimi i internetit në celular ka tejkaluar atë në desktop. Grupi ekspert i grafikës krijon një dizajn të posatshëm për paisjet mobile, i cili përfshin një menu minimale për ekranin e vogël.</p>\r\n<p>Për këtë vit vihet re tendenca e ndërtimit fillimisht të dizajnit të faqes web për paisjet mobile, dhe më pas dizenjimi i grafikës të faqes web për aplikacionet desktop. Vihet re tendenca që gjithnjë e më shumë faqe web do të strukturojnë përmbajtjen e tyre për ekranet e vegjël mobile, duke lënë si zgjedhje dytësore versionin e web-it për desktopit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',447,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Mobile first\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:499:\"<p>As the number of Smartphone’s users is increasing, the mobile browsing has surpassed the desktop browsing. Designers have already a design for the Smartphone, which includes a minimal menu for the small screen. As one of most used web design tends 2018, the mobile-first design is the process of designing for mobile first, then working up to the bigger ones.</p>\r\n<p>More and more sites will deliver their content to the smaller screens first, leaving secondary choice the desktop version.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',447,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(525,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,448,1566224352,1544308966,7,0,0,4608,'textpic','Ilustrime të personalizuara','','','<p>Ilustrimet janë të fantastike, përfundimisht. Artistë të grafikës arrijnë të bëjnë ilustrime të përshtatura për markën që ata përfaqësojnë. Ky trend i grafikës web është shumë i përshtatshëm për markat që janë argëtuese dhe energjike, por jo vetëm.</p>\r\n<p>Markat që perceptohen si tradicionale dhe serioze mund të jenë gjithashtu më tërheqëse duke përdorur këtë tendence grafike. Cilido qoftë identiteti i markës tuaj, ekziston gjithmonë një ilustrim grafik që e përfaqëson më së miri atë.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',448,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"Custom illustrations\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:414:\"<p>Illustrations are great, definitively. Professional artists can make illustrations tailored to the brand which they represent. This web design trend 2018 is awesome for brands which are fun and energetic, but not only them. Brands that are perceived as traditional and serious can be more attractive by using this trend.</p>\r\n<p>Whatever your brand identity is, there’s always an illustration to match it.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',448,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(526,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,449,1566224412,1544308966,7,0,0,4864,'textpic','E madhe ose hiç','','','<p>Një nga tendencat që po dominojnë qartë stilet e web për vitin 2018 është tipografia e guximshme. Shkrimet e mëdhenj po përdoren më së shumti në faqet e internetit. Ato shfrytëzojnë më mirë hapësirën e bardhë dhe tërheqin vëmendjen. Titujt e mëdhenj janë zgjedhur për të shfaqë më në pah mesazhin e markës.</p>\r\n<p>Roli i titujve në një faqe interneti është për të dhënë informacion që do të tërheqë vizitorin e faqes. Në tendencat aktuale të dizajnit të faqeve të internetit janë titujt shkrime kreative dhe të guximshme.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',449,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:14:\"Big or Nothing\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:398:\"<p>One of most notable web design trends 2018 is the bold typography. One reason is that the bigger fonts utilize better the white space, and draws attention. Big fonts are chosen to highlight the message of the brand. The role of the headers in a website is to order the information that will attract the visitor.</p>\r\n<p>In web design trends 2018, headers are full of creative bold typefaces.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',449,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(527,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,450,1566224466,1544308966,7,0,0,5120,'textpic','Asimetria dhe skemat e thyera','','','<p>Një tendencë eksperimentale e dizajnit të web është projektimi asimetrik dhe rrjetëzimet e thyera. Ato janë unike dhe të veçanta. Shumica e markave ende përdorin strukturat tradicionale të bazuara në paraqitjen e rrjetit të rregullt. Markat që duan të jenë unike tentojnë të provojnë efekte të ndryshme dhe do dalin jashtë skemave.</p>\r\n<p>Asimetria mund të jetë e bukur dhe harmonike. Ai jep një ndikim të veçantë tek vizitorët. Një shembull i këtij efekti në dizajn është faqja e internetit ku pamja asimetrike nuk është e balancuar në të dy anët e ekranit.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',450,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:33:\"Asymmetry and broken grid layouts\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:533:\"<p>The most experimental web design trend 2018 is the asymmetric design and broken grids. They are unique and distinctive. Most brands still use the traditional structures based on the grid layout, but the brands who want to be unique will try different layouts and will design out the box. Asymmetry can be both beautiful and harmonious. It gives a special impact to the visitors.</p>\r\n<p>One example of this web design trend 2018 is the website where the asymmetric layout is not perfectly balanced on the left and right sides.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',450,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(528,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,451,1566224523,1544308966,7,0,0,5376,'textpic','Animacionet e integruara','','','<p>Tendencat e dizajnit të web për vitin 2018 shkojnë përtej imazheve statike. Ato synojnë drejt animacioneve dhe efekteve multimediale. Përveç animacioneve në sfond të faqes, të cilat u përmenden më lart si animacione të grimcave, tendenca përfshin edhe animacione të vogla që shoqërojnë vizitorin përgjatë leximit të faqes web.</p>\r\n<p>Një animacion i vogël shkurton kohën e pritjes ndërsa faqja po ngarkohet. Gjithashtu, një animacion i vogël nxit lexuesin të lëvizë poshtë ose të fokusohet në një pjesë interesante të faqes web. Animacione të tilla janë mjete të fuqishme që vendosin vizitorin në rol kryesor gjatë lundrimit në web. Këto animacione të vogla krijojnë ndërveprime dinamike me vizitorin dhe e nxitin atë që të qëndrojë sa më gjatë në faqen web.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',451,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:21:\"Integrated animations\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:672:\"<p>Web design trends 2018 go further than static images, towards animations and multimedia effects. Besides the animations in the background, which are mentioned above as the particle animations, this trend includes small animations which accompany the visitor along the experience on the website. A small animation makes shorter the waiting time while the page is loading. Also, a small animation encourages to scroll down or to focus an interesting part of the web page. Such animations are powerful tools which include the visitor as an actor in whole website story. They create dynamic interactions with the visitor and encourage him to stay longer on the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',451,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(529,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,452,1566224571,1544308966,7,0,0,5632,'textpic','Shkallët dinamike','','','<p>Një nga rikthimet më të mëdha si tendencë e dizajnit web janë shkallët. Këtë herë, ata kthehen fuqishëm si efekt i preferuar, ku efekti gradient i bën ato misterioze dhe intriguese. Në një rast kur asnjë imazh nuk përshtatet me sfondin e faqes web, një gradient ngjyrash është zgjidhje interesante.</p>\r\n<p>Meqë web-i tashmë është i mbushur me efekte dinamike, gradientët dinamikë e përmbyllin këtë prirje eksperimentale të dizajnit në web. Një faqe e internetit mund të ketë një gradient kryesor të fiksuar në sfond i cili ju ndjek kudo ku jo shkoni në faqe.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',452,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Dynamic gradients\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:559:\"<p>One of the biggest comebacks as web design trends 2018 are of course the gradients. This time, they return loudly and colorful. The most popular effect is the gradient filter over photos, making them mysterious and intriguing. In a case when not any image fit with the background, the color gradient is an interesting solution. Since the modern web is packed with dynamic effects, dynamic gradients complete this experimental web design trend.</p>\r\n<p>This website has one main gradient fixed in the background and it follows you along while scrolling.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',452,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(530,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,453,1552437085,1544308966,7,0,0,5888,'textpic','Përmbledhje','','','<p>Tendencat e dizajnit web për vitin 2018 duket se janë me ngjyra dhe plot energji, diçka ndërmjet ngjyrave të ndezura, animacioneve të integruara dhe gradientëve dinamikë. Nuk dihet se deri ku do të shtyhet kufijtë tradicionale të grafikës web.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',453,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Summary\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:255:\"<p>Web design trends in 2018 seems to be both colorful and funny, something between bright colors, integrated animations and dynamic gradients. We can’t wait to see what designers are going to come up with and how they’re going to push the limits.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',453,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(531,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,396,1564493345,1544311745,7,0,0,1024,'textpic','Sistemi ECommerce in TYPO3','','','<p>TYPO3 è una soluzione per la maggior parte dei siti Web, in particolare per le aziende e i grandi negozi. Quale è la soluzione di TYPO3 per l\'e-commerce? Quali sono i principali sistemi di negozi TYPO3? Ci sono diverse soluzioni su come creare il tuo negozio online nel sito web in TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Esistono tre tipi principali di TYPO3 Extensions per l\'e-commerce:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>TYPO3 Extensions Native</li> 	<li>Widget</li> 	<li>Integrazioni con un altro software.</li> </ul>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',396,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:18:\"TYPO3 Shop Systems\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:464:\"<p>Nowadays, TYPO3 is the solution for most websites, especially for businesses and large companies. But what does TYPO3 offer as a solution for the e-commerce? Which are main TYPO3 shop systems? In fact, there are several solutions how to create your online store within your TYPO3 website. There are three main types of e-commerce TYPO3 extensions:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Native extensions</li> 	<li>Widgets</li> 	<li>Integrations with a third party software.</li> </ul>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',396,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(532,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,397,1566825170,1544311745,7,0,0,1280,'textpic','Sistemi di negozio TYPO3 implementati come estensioni native','','','<p>Con un TYPO3 Extensions Native, tu puoi gestire il negozio online dall\'interno dell sistema TYPO3, attraverso le proprie funzioni principali. Altre funzionalità come consegna o pagamento possono essere aggiunte a queste estensioni.</p>\r\n<p>Vi presentiamo una lista con le estensioni di TYPO3 che puoi usarli per implementare il tuo negozio online TYPO3:</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',397,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:51:\"TYPO3 shop systems implemented as Native Extensions\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:289:\"<p>Native extensions run the online shop inside the TYPO3 platform, within its own core functions. Extra functionality like deliver or pay the item can be added to these extensions. Below, it is a list with TYPO3 Native Extensions. You may use them to implement your TYPO3 online shop:</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',397,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(533,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,398,1564493385,1544311745,7,0,0,1536,'textpic','tt_products','','','<p>Questa TYPO3 Extension è un vecchio sistema di negozio TYPO3 offerto come software open source, dal 2007. Se vuoi personalizzare i progetti TYPO3 aggiungendo questo Extensions, forse ti troverai difficoltà come quale sara l\'implementazione di IVA per destinazioni diverse o come aggiungere i costi di spedizione per aree o pesi differenti.</p>\r\n<p>tt_products supporta queste funzionalità, ma ci vuole tempo e molto impegno per personalizzarle. tt_products ha un\'architettura vecchia, che usa il modello basato su Marker e le funzioni t3lib_div :: sono integrate con TYPO3 usando le estensioni wrapper.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su tt_products :<br /> Creato da Franz Holzinger<br /> Homepage https://www.ttproducts.de/<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/tt_products/<br /> Codice https://github.com/franzholz/tt_products</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',398,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"tt_products\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:809:\"<p>This extension is an old TYPO3 shop system offered as open software since 2007. If you try to customize TYPO3 projects adding this extension, you might encounter difficulties such as implementing different VAT for different destinations, or adding shipping cost for different regions or weight. tt_products supports these features, but it takes time and lot of effort to customize them.<br /> <br /> This extension has an outdated architecture. It uses the marker-based template and the t3lib_div:: functions are integrated with TYPO3 using the wrapper extensions.</p>\r\n<p>More details about tt_products : Maintainer Franz Holzinger<br /> Homepage https://www.ttproducts.de/<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/tt_products/<br /> Code https://github.com/franzholz/tt_products</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',398,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(534,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,399,1564493407,1544311745,7,0,0,1792,'textpic','Commerce','','','<p>Questo TYPO3 Extension è un software nativo di TYPO3 dal 2007, con un modello statico, che puoi integrarlo facilmente nel tuo sito web in TYPO3. Il codice si mantiene da Sebastian Fischer , e lavora sia per migliorare e aggiornare questa TYPO3 Extension. In futuro, Commerce sarà implementato in modello Fluid.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Commerce:<br /> Si mantiene da Sebastian Fischer<br /> Codice https://github.com/CommerceTeam/commerce</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',399,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:8:\"Commerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:441:\"<p>This TYPO3 extension is a native TYPO3 shop system since 2007. It comes with a static template and you can integrate it easily into your website. Its maintainer Sebastian Fischer works both for re-factoring the extension to an up-to-date implementation and also in moving it to the fluid based template.<br /> <br /> More detailes about Commerce :<br /> Maintainer Sebastian Fischer<br /> Code https://github.com/CommerceTeam/commerce</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',399,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(535,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,400,1564493429,1544311745,7,0,0,2048,'textpic','Cart','','','<p>Questo TYPO3 Extension è adattato per un negozio online con un numero limitato di articoli. Questo sistema di negozio TYPO3 è completamente funzionale, che include l\'elenco, la fatturazione, i pagamenti e i dettagli sulla spedizione dei prodotti. Lo sviluppatore lo configura manualmente.</p>\r\n<p>Cart usa il modello Fluid, che offre tutta la flessibilità del sistema TYPO3. Cart può essere personalizzato per fornire le funzionalità di pagamento o altre funzioni di consegna.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Cart:<br /> Homepage https://cart.extco.de<br /> Si mantiene da Daniel Lorenz<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/cart/<br /> Codice https://github.com/extcode/cart</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',400,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:4:\"Cart\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:682:\"<p>This TYPO3 extension is adapted for an online shop with a limited number of items. This TYPO3 shop system offers a fully functional e-commerce platform including product listing, billing, payments and product shipping details. The developer configures it manually. It uses fluid templates, which makes use of the power and flexibility of the TYPO3 system. Cart extension can be customized to provide extra payment functionality or other delivery functions.<br /> <br /> More details about Cart<br /> Homepage https://cart.extco.de<br /> Maintainer : Daniel Lorenz<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/cart/<br /> Code https://github.com/extcode/cart</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',400,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(536,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,401,1564493471,1544311745,7,0,0,2304,'textpic','Aimeos','','','<p>Questo TYPO3 Extension è basato sull Arcavias, un progetto che contiene una intera libreria di software per diversi sistemi di negozi online. Uno di questi è il sistema di negozio in TYPO3. Aimeos è una versione migliorata del codice di questa libreria. Aimeos include pacchetti per altri framework di sistemi di negozio come Laravel. In effetti, Aimeos può essere integrato nella maggior parte dei siti Web in PHP. La gestione di sessione dei messaggi di registrazione e altre funzionalità sono in codici in PHP.</p>\r\n<p>Aimeos include le funzionalità della infrastruttura TYPO3 per inviare e-mail, gestire le sessioni e generare gli URL. Il codice Aimeos per il framework TYPO3 non segue lo schema tipico dei nomi del database, come \"ext_tables.sql\" e il \"prefisso tx_\". Questo è uno dei problemi principali con Aimeos. Nel frattempo, il suo vantaggio è che puoi aggiungere molti prodotti nel tuo negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Aimeos:<br /> Homepage https://aimeos.org/<br /> Progetto aimeos<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/aimeos/<br /> Codice https://github.com/aimeos/aimeos-typo3</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',401,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:6:\"Aimeos\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1100:\"<p>This TYPO3 extension is based on Arcavias core which is a project that provides a library for different shop systems. One of them is TYPO3 shop system. Aimeos is an improved version of the code of this library. Aimeos includes packages for other shop systems frameworks such as Laravel. In fact, Aimeos can integrate into most PHP website. The logging messages session handler and other features are provided by the PHP code. When Aimeos is integrated with TYPO3, the TYPO3 infrastructure sends emails, handles the sessions and generates the URLs.<br /> <br /> The Aimeos code for the TYPO3 framework does not follow the typical database naming scheme, such as “ext_tables.sql” and the “tx_ prefix”. This is one of the main issues with Aimeos extension. Meanwhile, its advantage is that you can add in your store a wide range of products and many pricing structures.<br /> <br /> More details about Aimeos<br /> Homepage https://aimeos.org/<br /> Maintainer aimeos<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/aimeos/<br /> Code https://github.com/aimeos/aimeos-typo3</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',401,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(537,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,402,1564493496,1544311745,7,0,0,2560,'textpic','Multishop','','','<p>Multishop è un TYPO3 Extension che consente allo sviluppatore di modificare e gestire più negozi online all\'interno della stessa struttura di pagine. Il catalogo si mantiene completamente nella parte front-end. Il catalogo può essere facilmente modificato. Inoltre, tu può facilmente aggiungere o rimuovere categorie di prodotti e voci del menu di navigazione. Tutto questo grazie alla sua semplice interfaccia. Il venditore non ha bisogno di conoscere lo sviluppo web o TYPO3 per aggiornare e per gestire il suo negozio in TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Multishop: https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/multishop/</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',402,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:9:\"Multishop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:611:\"<p>Multishop is a TYPO3 shop extension which provides the web developer to edit and to manage multiple online shops within the same page tree. The maintenance of the catalog happens completely in the front of the website. The content manager can easily edit the product catalog. He also can easily add or remove product categories and navigation menu items. This is because of its friendly interface. The seller does not need to know web development or TYPO3 to update and to manage his TYPO3 shop.<br /> <br /> More details about Multishop you will find in https://extensions.typo3.org/extension/multishop/</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',402,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(538,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,403,1566825251,1544311745,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','Quick Shop','','','<p>Quick Shop è un Extension utile per la creazione di un nuovo negozio in TYPO3, molto pratico soprattutto per le piccole imprese. Quick Shop offre la possibilità di e-payment, una interfaccia di acquisto simile a Ebay, una galleria d\'immagini, e altri dettagli sul prodotto come la sua quantità nel negozio. Quick Shop include le funzionalità come l\'invio di una email al venditore, la consegna e la fatturazione, la posta elettronica al cliente.</p>\r\n<p>Quick Shop offre la possibilità di pubblicare le specifiche dell\'articolo in qualsiasi lingua. Inoltre Quick Shop è ottimizzato per i motori di ricerca (SEO). Questo TYPO3 Extension è una soluzione ottimale per le piccole imprese che non contengono molti prodotti, con molte specifiche, come il colore o le dimensioni. Purtroppo non si può gestire un negozio online molto complesso con Quick Shop.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Quick Shop :<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/quick_shop/Index.html</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',403,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Quick Shop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:929:\"<p>Quick Shop is a useful extension for building a TYPO3 shop, very practical expecially for a small business and small budget enterprises. This extension provides e-payment, shopping interface similar to ebay, image gallery and more product details like minimum or maximum quantities in the store. Quick Shop includes functionalities like sending an email to the seller, delivery and invoicing, email to the client and other helpful features.<br /> <br /> Quick Shop offers the possibility to publish the item specifications in any language. Also it is optimized for the search Engines (SEO). Quick Shop is an optimal solution for small businesses that do not contain a lot of products, with a lot of specifications, like colour or size. You cannot manage a complex online shop with Quick Shop.<br /> <br /> More details about Quick Shop :<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/quick_shop/Index.html</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',403,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(539,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,404,1556605843,1544311745,7,0,0,3072,'textpic','Sistemi di negozio TYPO3 implementati come Widget','','','<p>I Widget includono tutte le estensioni e gli elementi software collegati con servizi degli altri sistemi. Tali applicazioni includono l\'implementazione completa del negozio online, collegato alla piattaforma TYPO3.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',404,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:41:\"TYPO3 shop systems implemented as Widgets\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:199:\"<p>Widgets include all extensions and content elements that rely on third-party services. Such applications include the complete implementation of the online shop, linked with the TYPO3 platform.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',404,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(540,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,405,1566825329,1544311745,7,0,0,3200,'textpic','Supr','','','<p>Supr è un progetto di Wirecard, un partner di TYPO3 GmbH. Questo è un TYPO3 Extension che semplifica il processo di avvio di un nuovo negozio in TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Questi sono le istruzioni per avviare un nuovo negozio in TYPO3 con Supr:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>registrati in Supr</li> 	<li>aggiungi i prodotti del tuo negozio online</li> 	<li>seleziona lo stile</li> 	<li>installa il widget Supr sul tuo sito web TYPO3</li> 	<li>metti un link ai tuoi prodotti su Supr</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Il pagamento è implementato nel widget, ma puoi personalizzare la spedizione del prodotto e altre funzionalità del negozio online.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Supr:<br /> Homepage https://www.supr.com/&nbsp;<br /> Si mantiene da TYPO3 GmbH<br /> Documentazione https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/supr/&nbsp;<br /> Codice https://bitbucket.typo3.com/projects/SUPR/repos/supr/browse</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',405,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:4:\"Supr\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:801:\"<p>Supr is a project of Wirecard, a TYPO3 GmbH partner. It is a TYPO3 extension and makes easier the process of starting a new shop in TYPO3. You should follow these steps :</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>register at Supr</li> 	<li>add the products of your online store</li> 	<li>select the theme of your online store</li> 	<li>install the Supr widget on your TYPO3 website</li> 	<li>add links to your products on Supr</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The payment functionality is implemented in the widget, but you can customize the product shipping and other features of the online shop.<br /> <br /> More details about Supr<br /> Homepage https://www.supr.com/<br /> Maintainer TYPO3 GmbH<br /> Documentation https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/supr/<br /> Code https://bitbucket.typo3.com/projects/SUPR/repos/supr/browse</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',405,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(541,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,406,1566825387,1544311745,7,0,0,3264,'textpic','Widget offerti da Amazon','','','<p>Amazon offre \"Fulfillment by Amazon\" che è un insieme di servizi che integrano fatturazione, spedizione e altre funzionalità nel negozio TYPO3. I widget Amazon non sono solo per il sistema TYPO3, ma possono essere integrati in diversi sistemi web.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su Widgets offerti da Amazon:<br /> Homepage https://affiliate-program.amazon.co.uk/<br /> Amazon FBA https://services.amazon.co.uk/</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',406,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:25:\"Widgets offered by Amazon\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:438:\"<p>Amazon offers the \"Fulfilment by Amazon\" which is a set of services that integrate services such as billing, shipping and other functionality in the TYPO3 shop. Amazon widgets are not only for the TYPO3 platform, but they can be integrated into several web environments.<br /> <br /> More details about Widgets offered by Amazon<br /> Homepage https://affiliate-program.amazon.co.uk/<br /> Amazon FBA https://services.amazon.co.uk/</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',406,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(542,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,407,1556605874,1544311745,7,0,0,3296,'textpic','Sistemi di negozio TYPO3 implementati come integrazioni con un altro software.','','','<p>L\'integrazione con un secondo software implementa il negozio online in un altro sistema come Magento, Oxid o Shopware, con un collegamento esterno al sito web TYPO3.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',407,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:76:\"TYPO3 shop systems implemented as integrations with a thirds party software.\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:172:\"<p>Integration with a third party software implements the online shop in another platform such as Magento, Oxid or Shopware, with an external link to the TYPO3 Website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',407,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(543,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,408,1566825587,1544311745,7,0,0,3312,'textpic','Integrazione con Shopware: px_shopware','','','<p>Questo software è un Extension offerto da Portrino GmbH, che integra TYPO3 con Shopware. TYPO3 offre la navigazione, gestione dei contenuti e modulo di accesso. Il login nell\'account Shopware utilizza l\'API HybridAuth. Questo Extension include la gestione di contenuti TYPO3 con i collegamenti ai prodotti del negozio online. Tu puoi inserire i dettagli del prodotto come un normale contenuto di TYPO3.</p>\r\n<p>Dettagli su px_shopware:<br /> Homepage http://www.portrino.de/<br /> Creato da Portrino GmbH<br /> Codice https://github.com/portrino/px_shopware</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',408,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:38:\"Integration with Shopware: px_shopware\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:559:\"<p>This software is a third party extension offered by Portrino GmbH. It integrates TYPO3 with Shopware. TYPO3 provides navigation, content management and login form. The login in the Shopware account uses the HybridAuth API. This extension includes in the TYPO3 content manager with the links to the products of the online store. Editors insert product details like a normal TYPO3 content.<br /> <br /> More details about px_shopware<br /> Homepage http://www.portrino.de/<br /> Maintainer Portrino GmbH<br /> Code https://github.com/portrino/px_shopware</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',408,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(544,18,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,409,1564493683,1544311745,7,0,0,3320,'textpic','Integrazione con Magento: Mate','','','<p>Questo Extension utilizza Magento come il sistema principale di e-commerce, ma il contenuto viene inserito da TYPO3. Quando TYPO3 serve la pagina web, viene consegnato solo il contenuto di TYPO3. Il contenuto consegnato da Magento può essere arricchito dai contenuti del CMS.</p>\r\n<p>Detagli su Mate:</p>\r\n<p>Homepage https://www.maxserv.com/mate/&nbsp;<br /> Codice https://github.com/MaxServ/MATE</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',409,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:30:\"Integration with Magento: Mate\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:446:\"<p>This extension uses Magento as the main e-commerce platform, but the content is fetched from TYPO3. When TYPO3 serves the webpage, only the TYPO3 content 