0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',417,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:19:\"Trend and actuality\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:228:\"<p>Actually, TYPO3 is the CMS used by 130,998 websites. It is free to use. Meanwhile, WordPress is the CMS used by 27,449,706 websites. It is also free to use, and it is well known as a semantic personal publishing platform.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:400;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:2;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:1;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',417,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(551,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,418,1564492241,1544313715,7,0,0,1792,'textpic','Un sistema facile da usare','','','<p>TYPO3 offre una facile gestione dei contenuti. L\'utente mette al posto il menu, il contenuto e le pagine, solo con il click.</p>\r\n<p>WordPress è facilissimo come il suo nome. È per questo che ogni blogger lo adora. Non è necessario sapere nessun trucco tecnologico per aggiungere i contenuti nel sito web.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',418,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Simplicity\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:322:\"<p>TYPO3 offers an easy implementation of content management. The user will just drag and drop the menu, content, and pages in the dashboard. WordPress shows the simplicity in its own name. It is user-friendly and each blogger loves it. You don’t need to master any technological tool to add content in your website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:400;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',418,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(552,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,419,1564492270,1544313715,7,0,0,2048,'textpic','Una grafica relattiva','','','<p>TYPO3 offre una grafica relattivo su suoi modelli, che sono indipendenti dalla funzionalità. È possibile aggiungere nuove funzionalità utilizzando l\'estensione TYPO3. Questo CMS offre mille opzioni per la creare un sito Web completamente unico.</p>\r\n<p>WordPress crea la funzionalità utilizzando gli WordPress Extensions. Nel frattempo, la grafica del sito in WordPress si crea con un tema in WordPress. Non esiste una indipendenza tra le estensioni e il tema WordPress scelta dall esperto di grafica. Alcune funzioni sono correlati al tema.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',419,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Responsive Layout\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:595:\"<p>TYPO3 builds a responsive layout upon TYPO3 templates, which are core independent. Extra functionality could be added by using the TYPO3 extension. This CMS offers unlimited possibilities for building a fully optional website. WordPress builds the functionality by using WordPress Extensions.<br /> <br /> Meanwhile, the design of the website in WordPress is the style of a WordPress theme. But there does not exist a full independence between the extensions used by the developer and the WordPress Theme chosen by the designer. Certain features are dependent on and related to the theme.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:400;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:2;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',419,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(553,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,420,1564492288,1544313715,7,0,0,2304,'textpic','La ripresentazione della azienda','','','<p>TYPO3 è molto adatto per grandi siti Web delle aziende.</p>\r\n<p>Nel frattempo, WordPress è il CMS creato per qualsiasi sito Web. WordPress è molto usato in blog personali e in piccoli siti Web delle aziende.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',420,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:26:\"The purpose of the website\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:261:\"<p>TYPO3 is very suitable for large websites used for companies or businesses. Meanwhile, WordPress is the CMS used in the very beginning of any website, for different purposes. WordPress is very used in personal blogs, small websites, or business websites.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',420,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(554,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,421,1564492310,1544313715,7,0,0,2560,'textpic','Sicurezza','','','<p>TYPO3 offre molte funzionalità integrate per gestire la sicurezza del sito Web.</p>\r\n<p>WordPress offre la sua sicurezza ottimale quando il sistema è regolarmente aggiornato.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',421,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:8:\"Security\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:145:\"<p>TYPO3 offers a set of built-in features for security. WordPress provides its optimal security when the system is updated on regular basis.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:300;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:2;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',421,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(555,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,422,1564493250,1544313715,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','La struttura del sito','','','<p>TYPO3 organizza le pagine in una struttura simile alle cartelle in un filesystem.</p>\r\n<p>WordPress elenca tutte le pagine una sotto l\'altra.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',422,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:16:\"Layout structure\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:140:\"<p>TYPO3 organizes the pages in a tree-structure, similar to the folders in a filesystem. WordPress lists all pages one under the other.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',422,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(556,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,423,1544314146,1544313715,7,0,0,3072,'textpic','Qual è la migliore, TYPO3 o WordPress?','','','<p>Per molte ragioni, non esiste una rivalità diretta tra TYPO3 e WordPress. Questi due sistemi si usano per i siti Web deferenti.</p>\r\n<p>I nostri esperti Web suggeriscono che è meglio scegliere WordPress se:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Il tuo sito web è relativamente semplice, con alcune funzionalità elementari.</li> 	<li>Vuoi spendere poco e preferisci gestire da solo il tuo sito web.</li> 	<li>Il tuo sito web non ha bisogno di essere in lingue straniere.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>TYPO3 è il CMS giusto se:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Il tuo sito web è organizzato in una struttura complessa di pagine e sotto-pagine.</li> 	<li>Il tuo sito web sarà la promozione della tua attività in molte lingue.</li> 	<li>Ci dovrebbero essere dati integrati da altre sorse.</li> 	<li>Vuoi spendere una somma media di soldi sul tuo sito Web, per assistenza nella progettazione, realizzazione e manutenzione.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>W3DEVELOPMENT è un gruppo di esperti Web che ti può garantire che siete sulla giusta strada per avere successo con la ripresentazione della azienda nel Web.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',423,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"the best CMS\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1216:\"<p>Which one is the best, TYPO3 or WordPress?</p>\r\n<p>For many reasons, there is no direct competition between TYPO3 and WordPress. They differ in the types of the websites they suite, and both of them lead the respective fields.<br /> <br /> You better choose WordPress if :</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Your website is relatively simple, with some basic features.</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You have a small or a medium budget, and you prefer to manage yourself the website.</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Your website does not need to be in multiple languages.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>TYPO3 is the right CMS if:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Your website is organized in a complex structure of pages and sub-pages.</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Your website will be the promotion of your business in many languages.</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; There should be data integrated from other sources.</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You have a medium to large budget to spend on your website for assistance with the design, build and maintenance.</li> </ul>\r\n<p>W3DEVELOPMENT do have expertise web developers with business excellence, so we can guarantee you will be guided to right track to succeed in your business.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',423,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(557,17,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,424,1548609566,1544313715,7,0,0,3200,'html','','','','<div class=\"container\">\r\n          <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col\">\r\n              <div class=\"blog-posts single-post\">\r\n                <article class=\"post post-large blog-single-post\">\r\n                  <div class=\"post-content\">\r\n                    <div class=\"post-block post-share\">\r\n                      <h3 class=\"heading-primary\"><i class=\"fa fa-share\"></i>Condividi</h3>\r\n                      <!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->\r\n                      <div class=\"addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style \">\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_button_facebook_like\" fb:like:layout=\"button_count\"></a>\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_button_tweet\"></a>\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_button_pinterest_pinit\"></a>\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_counter addthis_pill_style\"></a>\r\n                      </div>\r\n        