l\">\r\n              <div class=\"blog-posts single-post\">\r\n                <article class=\"post post-large blog-single-post\">\r\n                  <div class=\"post-content\">\r\n                    <div class=\"post-block post-share\">\r\n                      <h3 class=\"heading-primary\"><i class=\"fa fa-share\"></i>Share this post</h3>\r\n                      <!-- AddThis Button BEGIN -->\r\n                      <div class=\"addthis_toolbox addthis_default_style \">\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_button_facebook_like\" fb:like:layout=\"button_count\"></a>\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_button_tweet\"></a>\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_button_pinterest_pinit\"></a>\r\n                        <a class=\"addthis_counter addthis_pill_style\"></a>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=xa-50faf75173aadc53\"></script>\r\n                      <!-- AddThis Button END -->\r\n                    </div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                </article>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\";s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',454,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(574,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,443,1564491328,1544315326,7,0,0,1024,'textpic','Tendenze web mobile','','','<p>Gli esperti della grafica web si affrontano con le sfide tecniche e continuano a creare siti eleganti e flessibili allo stesso tempo.</p>\r\n<p>Nel 2017 la navigazione mobile ha fatto molti progressi. Ora ci sono più utenti che navigano dal mobile rispetto alla navigazione desktop. Questo è il motivo per cui il nel 2018 vedremo delle funzionalità in mobile in nuovi modi.</p>\r\n<p>Diamo un\'occhiata ad alcune tendenze del web design nel 2018.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',443,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Mobile web trends\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:512:\"<p>Web designers deal with the technical challenges that are large in number, and still continue to create user-friendly sites, stylish and flexible with every device and just beautiful all at once. 2017 made more advancement in mobile browsing, who now counts more users than desktop browsing. This is a reason why 2018 is going to have fully mobile functionalities in new ways. Meanwhile, desktops will evolve in such way to stay relevant.</p>\r\n<p>So, let’s take a look at some web design trends in 2018.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',443,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(575,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,444,1566222295,1544315326,7,0,0,1280,'textpic','Le ombre','','','<p>Le ombre sono una tecnica grafica tradizionale, ma recentemente è ridimensionata come una tendenza del web design nel 2018. Le ombre mette in luce l\'importanza di progettare il web in uno spazio tridimensionale. Nell\'elenco delle tendenze del web design nel 2018, si notano griglie spezzate, animazioni, illustrazioni e grandi caratteri. Tutti questi effetti grafici sono molto differenti dal minimalismo, che era una tendenza dell qualche anno fa.</p>\r\n<p>Il concetto di profondità nel grafico dà al sito web la sensazione unica e un\'impressione memorabile. Questo effetto crea un senso di una immagine reale. Le ombre applicano in sfondo web, in logo o in qualsiasi rappresentazione grafica. L\'effetto della profondità in una pagina piatta può essere uno strumento potente per mettere in focus un elemento grafico.</p>\r\n<p>Con la prospettiva di profondità, l\'intero disegno otterrà più attenzione. In questo esempio, la tralucente aggiunge un effetto di profondità e crea una prospettiva dall\'alto verso il basso.</p>\r\n<p class=\"western\">&nbsp;</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',444,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:22:\"Drop shadows and depth\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:998:\"<p>Drop shadows are an old graphical technique, but it’s the newly implemented as web design trend in 2018, and it highlights the importance of designing the web in a three-dimensional space. In the list of web design trends 2018, you will notice broken grids, animations, illustrations and big fonts. All these graphical effects differ a lot from the minimalism which was a trend during past years.</p>\r\n<p>The concept of the depth in the graphic gives to the website the unique feeling and a memorable impression. It creates the sense of a real image, even if it is an abstract one. This effect is a web design trend in 2018 applied in web background, logo or any other graphical representation. The effect of depth in a flat page can be also a powerful tool to emphasize an element in the design. The whole design will get more attention when used this depth perspective.</p>\r\n<p>In this example, playing with translucency adds depth effect, and creates an impressive top-down perspective.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',444,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(576,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,445,1566222569,1544315326,7,0,0,1536,'textpic','Combinazioni di colori vibranti e saturi','','','<p>Le tendenze del web design nel 2018 sono assolutamente piene di super colori. Negli anni passati, marchi e designer hanno utilizzato maggiormente i \"colori sicuri per il web\". In quest\'anno gli esperti della grafica sono diventati più coraggiosi nel loro approccio su colore, esperimentanocon la super-saturazione e le tonalità vivaci.</p>\r\n<p>A parte i colori, i titoli nel web non sono più solo orizzontali ma ridimensionati con barre e angolari.I colori vibranti sono un suggerimento ai nuovi marchi, perché attirano immediatamente l\'attenzione degli utenti. Questa tendenza può essere perfetta anche le marche che vogliono allontanare la loro grafica da quella tradizionale.</p>\r\n<p>I colori saturi attirano l\'attenzione, specialmente se utilizzati in avvisi e notifiche. Per esempio, un colore rosso può essere mescolato con una tonalità blu. Il sito sembra professionale, e affatto noioso.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',445,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:35:\"Vibrant and saturated color schemes\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:932:\"<p>Web design trends 2018 are absolutely full of super excess colors online. In the past years, brands and designers used more the “web-safe colors”. In this year, web designers are becoming more courageous in their approach to color—including super-saturation and vibrant shades. Apart the colors, web headers are no longer just horizontal but resized with slashes and hard angles.</p>\r\n<p>Vibrant colors as web design trends in 2018 are suggested to the new brands because they attract immediately the attention of the users. This trend can be also perfect for every brand who wants to distant their design from the traditional one.</p>\r\n<p>The effect of saturated colors is the attraction of the attention, especially when used in buttons, links, alerts, and notifications. In this example, is chosen a striking red color and mixed with blues and navy tones. The site looks very professional, not dull or boring at all.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',445,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(577,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,446,1566223545,1544315326,7,0,0,1792,'textpic','Sfondo di particelle','','','<p>Una delle tendenze del web design nel 2018 è uno sfondo che contiene piccoli, semplici forme, immagini complessi e animazioni di particelle. Gli effetti potrebbero essere cerchi, triangoli o altre forme geometriche. La grafica include una scena dinamica, con queste particelle che si muovono attorno a qualcosa, vibrano, ballano o reagiscono alle azioni dell\'utente.</p>\r\n<p>Il ruolo principale di tutto questo scenario è quello di dare alla grafica un effetto di movimento e una vibrazione geometrica.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',446,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"Particle backgrounds\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:483:\"<p>One of the web design trends 2018 is the backgrounds containing simple dots, simple geometric shapes, complex images and particles animations. The effects might be vibrant balls, few circles, and a lot of plain triangles or other geometric shapes. The design includes a dynamic scene, when these particles move around something, vibrate, dance, or react to the user’s actions.</p>\r\n<p>The main role of all this scenery is to give the interface a motion and a geometric vibe.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',446,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(578,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,447,1566223140,1544315326,7,0,0,2048,'textpic','Prima di tutto la grafica web nel mobile','','','<p>Con l\'aumento del numero di utenti di smartphone, la navigazione mobile ha superato la navigazione sul desktop. Gli esperti della grafica realizzano prima un design per lo smartphone, che include un menu per il piccolo schermo.</p>\r\n<p>Nel 2018, prima si crea la grafica e il contenuto per gli schermi più piccoli, e poi, come una scelta secondaria, la versione per il desktop.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',447,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:12:\"Mobile first\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:499:\"<p>As the number of Smartphone’s users is increasing, the mobile browsing has surpassed the desktop browsing. Designers have already a design for the Smartphone, which includes a minimal menu for the small screen. As one of most used web design tends 2018, the mobile-first design is the process of designing for mobile first, then working up to the bigger ones.</p>\r\n<p>More and more sites will deliver their content to the smaller screens first, leaving secondary choice the desktop version.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',447,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(579,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,448,1566223367,1544315326,7,0,0,2304,'textpic','Illustrazioni personalizzate','','','<p>Le illustrazioni sono definitivamente fantastiche. Gli professionisti in design possono realizzare illustrazioni personalizzati per il marchio che rappresentano. Questa tendenza del web design nel 2018 è sopratutto per i marchi divertenti ed energici, ma non solo.</p>\r\n<p>I marchi che sono sempre percepiti come tradizionali possono essere più attraenti se utilizzano questa tendenza. Qualunque sia la identità della marca, c\'è sempre un\'illustrazione personalizzata che gli dà una nuova dimensione.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',448,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:20:\"Custom illustrations\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:414:\"<p>Illustrations are great, definitively. Professional artists can make illustrations tailored to the brand which they represent. This web design trend 2018 is awesome for brands which are fun and energetic, but not only them. Brands that are perceived as traditional and serious can be more attractive by using this trend.</p>\r\n<p>Whatever your brand identity is, there’s always an illustration to match it.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',448,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(580,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,449,1566223509,1544315326,7,0,0,2560,'textpic','Un font grande o niente','','','<p>Una delle più importanti tendenze del web design nel 2018 è la tipografia di grande font.I caratteri più grandi utilizzano meglio lo spazio bianco e attirano l\'attenzione. Loro vengono scelti per evidenziare il messaggio del marchio.</p>\r\n<p>Per questo anno, le intestazioni sono piene di caratteri tipografici audaci e creativi.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',449,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:14:\"Big or Nothing\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:398:\"<p>One of most notable web design trends 2018 is the bold typography. One reason is that the bigger fonts utilize better the white space, and draws attention. Big fonts are chosen to highlight the message of the brand. The role of the headers in a website is to order the information that will attract the visitor.</p>\r\n<p>In web design trends 2018, headers are full of creative bold typefaces.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',449,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(581,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,450,1566223704,1544315326,7,0,0,2816,'textpic','Asimmetria','','','<p>La tendenza più sperimentale del web design nel 2018 è il design asimmetrico. La maggior parte delle marche utilizza ancora le strutture tradizionali, ma i marchi che vogliono essere unici proveranno layout diversi. L\'asimmetria può essere bella e armoniosa. Lei dà un impatto speciale ai visitatori.</p>\r\n<p>Un esempio di questa tendenza è il sito web in cui il layout asimmetrico non è perfettamente bilanciato su lato sinistro e destro.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',450,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:33:\"Asymmetry and broken grid layouts\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:533:\"<p>The most experimental web design trend 2018 is the asymmetric design and broken grids. They are unique and distinctive. Most brands still use the traditional structures based on the grid layout, but the brands who want to be unique will try different layouts and will design out the box. Asymmetry can be both beautiful and harmonious. It gives a special impact to the visitors.</p>\r\n<p>One example of this web design trend 2018 is the website where the asymmetric layout is not perfectly balanced on the left and right sides.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',450,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(582,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,451,1566223831,1544315326,7,0,0,3072,'textpic','Animazioni integrate','','','<p>Le tendenze del web design nel 2018 vanno oltre le immagini statiche, verso le animazioni e gli effetti multimediali.Questa tendenza include piccole animazioni che accompagnano il visitatore durante l\'esperienza sul sito web.</p>\r\n<p>Una piccola animazione riduce il tempo di attesa durante il caricamento della pagina. Inoltre, una piccola animazione incoraggia l\'utente a scorrere verso il basso o a mettere in centro dell attenzione una parte interessante della pagina web. Tali animazioni sono strumenti che trasforma il visitatore in un attore nell\'intera storia del sito web.</p>\r\n<p>Queste animazioni incoraggiano il visitatore a rimanere più a lungo sul sito web.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',451,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:21:\"Integrated animations\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:672:\"<p>Web design trends 2018 go further than static images, towards animations and multimedia effects. Besides the animations in the background, which are mentioned above as the particle animations, this trend includes small animations which accompany the visitor along the experience on the website. A small animation makes shorter the waiting time while the page is loading. Also, a small animation encourages to scroll down or to focus an interesting part of the web page. Such animations are powerful tools which include the visitor as an actor in whole website story. They create dynamic interactions with the visitor and encourage him to stay longer on the website.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',451,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(583,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,452,1566224013,1544315326,7,0,0,3200,'textpic','Gradienti dinamici','','','<p>Questa volta, le sfumature ritornano più colorate che mai. L\'effetto più popolare è il filtro sfumato sulle foto, rendendole misteriose e intriganti. In un caso in cui nessuna immagine si adatta allo sfondo, il gradiente colorato è una soluzione interessante.</p>\r\n<p>Poiché il web moderno è pieno di effetti dinamici, i gradienti dinamici completano questa tendenza sperimentale del web design. Per esempio il sito ha una sfumatura principale fissa sullo sfondo, che ti segue mentre scorri in basso.</p>',0,0,0,0,1,730,8,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',452,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:17:\"Dynamic gradients\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:559:\"<p>One of the biggest comebacks as web design trends 2018 are of course the gradients. This time, they return loudly and colorful. The most popular effect is the gradient filter over photos, making them mysterious and intriguing. In a case when not any image fit with the background, the color gradient is an interesting solution. Since the modern web is packed with dynamic effects, dynamic gradients complete this experimental web design trend.</p>\r\n<p>This website has one main gradient fixed in the background and it follows you along while scrolling.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;}',452,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(584,14,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,453,1556602320,1544315326,7,0,0,3264,'textpic','Conclusione','','','<p>I trend che domineranno il web design nel 2018 sembrano essere sia colorati che divertenti, con animazioni integrati e sfumature dinamiche. Siamo curiosi di vedere cosa riusciranno a creare i designer e come faranno a spingere oltre i limiti.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,'',0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',453,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Summary\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:255:\"<p>Web design trends in 2018 seems to be both colorful and funny, something between bright colors, integrated animations and dynamic gradients. We can’t wait to see what designers are going to come up with and how they’re going to push the limits.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\