0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',620,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Preface\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:547:\"<p>Most of the ecommerce frameworks used presently are inexpensive or free. The open-source platforms are worthy as they are not only free but also managed and developed by experienced people across the globe. It is advisable to decide about the experience you require from your online store that may be a self-hosting or complete package at a small fee, etc. People use open-source platforms as they are packed with unique features and developer friendly. Let’s discuss top 10 important open-source ecommerce platforms to watch out in 2019.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',620,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(796,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,621,1567427643,1567427542,10,0,0,960,'textpic','Magento 2','','','<p>Magento bazohet kod PHP, i cili ndihmon në ndërtimin e algoritmeve të përshkallëzuara. Kjo platformë vjen e mbushur me plugins dhe extensions, të cilat mund të integrohen lehtësisht me aplikacionet e palëve të treta. Magento 2 është ndërtuar për zhvilluesit, kështu që ata nuk kanë pse të nisin kodin nga e para. Përdoruesi i kësaj platforme ka nevojë për eksperience programimi në PHP. Magento vjen me dy versione: Magento 1 dhe Magento 2. Versioni Magento 2 është risia e fundit, pasi më shumë se 200,000 shitës me pakicë në internet e përdorin këtë version. Ai ofron mjete për të mundësuar marketingun, menaxhimin e katalogut dhe nevojat e SEO.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',621,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:9:\"Magento 2\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:577:\"<p>Magento is based upon the PHP-based framework that helps in building scalable solutions. This platform comes packed with multiple plugins and extensions that can be easily integrated with the third-party apps. As it is built for the developers, so they do not have to start from scratch. The user needs expertise in PHP Programming. The Magento had two versions Magento 1 and Magento 2. The Magento 2 version is the latest development as more than 200,000 online retailers use it. This version offers tools to cover advanced marketing, catalog management, and SEO needs.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',621,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(797,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,622,1567427765,1567427542,10,0,0,992,'textpic','WooCommerce','','','<p>WooCommerce është një plugin në WordPress, i cili ka karakteristika dhe funksionalitete të thjeshta për përdoruesit. Ai mund të shkarkohet falas dhe ka funksionalitete të jashtëzakonshme të zgjerueshme. Nëse dëshironi të filloni një faqe të suksesshme shitjesh online, ju rekomandojmë platformën WooCommerce për thjeshtësinë që ofron. Ajo siguron shumë mundësi në ndërtimin e një dyqani të mahnitshëm, me një fleksibilitet mjaft të madh. WooCommerce është profesional, i thjeshtë, me WooThemes të fundit dhe me opsione të reja. Ajo lidh të gjitha portat kryesore me faqen tuaj te internetit. WooCommerce gjithashtu mund të lidhet me Stripe dhe me PayPal, të cilat janë portat e paracaktuara për pagesën online.</p>\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',622,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"WooCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:595:\"<p>WooCommerce is a WordPress plugin that has user-friendly features and functionalities. It is free to download and renders enormous extendible features. If you want to start a perfect E-Commerce startup with a great website, then it is easily understandable and highly recommended. It provides plenty of options that support in building an amazing store with greater flexibility. It’s professional, simple, possess latest WooThemes, and has many customization options. It connects all the major gateways to your website. It also renders Stripe and PayPal as the default payment gateways.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',622,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(798,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,628,1567427819,1567427542,10,0,0,1008,'textpic','Aimeos','','','<p>Aimeos është një librari me kod të hapur, në PHP. Duke qënë një framework për e-Commerce, ajo ofron një seri përbërësish për aplikacionet e dyqaneve online. Aimeos është e integruar në komponentë të thjeshtë për t’u përdorur, që janë të disponueshëm për një gamë të gjerë framework. Integrimet e saj ekzistuese përfshijnë:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Extension i TYPO3 Web Shop</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paketa Laravel E-Commerce</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paketa Flow Online shop</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Paketa SlimPHP E-Commerce</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Karakteristikat kryesore platformës Aimeos konsistojnë në integrim të thjeshtë, veprime më të shpejta, aftësi për menaxhimin e shumë dyqaneve, funksione shumë të shkallëzueshme, fleksibilitet si dhe optimizimi për paisjet mobile.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',628,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:6:\"Aimeos\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:643:\"<p>It is open-source PHP library and an E-Commerce framework offering a set of featured components for online shop applications. The Aimeos is integrated into simple to use components that are available for a wide range of frameworks. Its existing integrations include:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>TYPO3 Web shop extension</li> 	<li>Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>Laravel E-Commerce package</li> 	<li>Flow Online shop package</li> 	<li>SlimPHP E-Commerce package</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The main features of this platform consist of easy integration, faster operations, multi-store capability, highly scalable, flexible, mobile optimized, and configurable.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',628,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(799,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,630,1567427856,1567427542,10,0,0,1016,'textpic','osCommerce','','','<p>osCommerce është në tregun e platformave e-Commerce për 15 vitet e fundit. Ajo është parë si një mundësi e vjetër, e besueshme për shumë biznese të vogla dhe startup-e.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo platformë e-Commerce ofron më shumë se 7,000 integrime falas me 13,000 dyqane online, të cilat funksionojnë në këtë platformë.</p>\r\n<p>Sipas një studimi, osCommerce është e 11-ta më e popullarizuara në mesin e 1 milion site-ve, në kategorinë me kod të hapur.<br /> Shitësit me pakicë në internet e përdorin osCommerce për lehtësinë që ofron në ndërtimin një dyqani online, lehtësisht të menaxhueshëm.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo platformë integrohet me të gjitha aplikacionet e palëve të treta, duke paraqitur faqen tuaj në Web në gjuhë të ndryshme.<br /> Ju mund të gjeni një numër të madh programuesish në komunitetin e osCommerce, të cilët jua lehtësojnë procesin e zhvillimit, dhe pse osCommerce nuk është aspak komplekse.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',630,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"OsCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:788:\"<p>OsCommerce is into the business for the last 15 years. It is seen as an old reliable option for many small businesses and startups to get seamless features.</p>\r\n<p>This E-Commerce platform renders more than 7,000 free integrations with 13,000 stores running on this platform.</p>\r\n<p>According to a <a href=\"https://trends.builtwith.com/shop/osCommerce\">study</a>, it is 11th most popular amongst Top 1 million sites in the open-source category.<br /> The online retailers use it for its ease to design a well-managed online shop.</p>\r\n<p>This platform easily integrates with all the third-party apps, presents your online site in multiple languages.<br /> You can find a vast number of community developers to ease out your development process, and OsCommerce is not all complex.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',630,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(800,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,631,1567427919,1567427542,10,0,0,1020,'textpic','xtCommerce','','','<p>Kjo është një platformë e re në tregun e e-Commerce. Ajo është me kod të hapur, e përdorur nga mjaft biznese online në ditët e sotme. Zhvillimi i vazhdueshëm i përmirëson funksionalitetet e kësaj platformë.</p>\r\n<p>xtCommerce ju ndihmon të promovoni një numër të pakufizuar të produkteve në internet. Ju mund të krijoni nën-seksione të këtyre produkteve për t\'i shfaqur ato me lehtësi.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo zgjidhje me kod të hapur siguron opsionin e një dyqani ndërkombëtar në gjuhë të ndryshme, menaxhon kategori të pakufizuara, me një ndërfaqe të thjeshtë, etj. xtCommerce, gjithashtu, ndihmon në krijimin e përgjigjeve të Cart2Cart ndaj kërkesave të tregtarëve online.</p>\r\n<p>Nëse nuk jeni të sigurt për integrimin e kësaj platforme E-Commerce, atëherë mund të jua besoni ndërtimin e dyqanit online profesionisteve të xtCommerce, duke e kaluar si shërbim outsource.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',631,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"xtCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:703:\"<p>This is a newer open-source <em><strong>ecommerce</strong></em> platform used by the business houses nowadays. The ongoing development is done with this platform to enhance its functionalities.</p>\r\n<p>This platform helps the store owners to promote an unlimited number of products online. You can even create sub-sections of these products to display them with ease.</p>\r\n<p>This open-source solution renders multilingual support, manage unlimited categories, easy to navigate interface, etc. xtCommerce also helps in making Cart2Cart responses to the requirements of e-merchants.</p>\r\n<p>If you are not aware of integrating this E-Commerce platform, then you can outsource the related services.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',631,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(801,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,632,1567427992,1567427542,10,0,0,1022,'textpic','WP E-Commerce','','','<p>Kjo platformë mbahet si \"zgjidhja origjinale për e-Commerce\" për WordPress. Zhvilluesit e kanë shkarkuar WP E-Commerce më shumë se 3 milion herë. Kodi për këtë plugin në WordPress është mjaft i thjeshtë. Nëse jeni profesionistë në HTML dhe CSS, atëherë mund ta trajtoni lehtësisht këtë plugin. Shitësit me pakicë në internet mund të marrin mbështetje nga agjensi të njohura për zhvillimin e WordPress, ose mund t\'i drejtohen për mbështetje komunitetit të madh të zhvilluesve online. Shembuj të WP E-Commerce janë Mayrun’s Goods, MollyMeg, dhe Cronut.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',632,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"WP E-Commerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:522:\"<p>This plugin boasts as the “original E-Commerce solution” for WordPress. The developers have downloaded the WP E-Commerce more than 3 million times. The coding for this WordPress plugin is quite simple. If you are good at HTML and CSS, then you can handle this plugin with utmost ease. The online retailers can take support from the reputed WordPress development agency or can turn to the large community of online developers for support. The examples of WP E-Commerce are Mayrun’s Goods, MollyMeg, and Cronut.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',632,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(802,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,633,1567428031,1567427542,10,0,0,1023,'textpic','PrestaShop','','','<p>PrestaShop është një platformë e re në E-Commerce, por po bëhet mjaft e njohur për shkak të instalimit, aksesit të lehtë dhe ndërfaqes të pëlqyer nga përdoruesit.</p>\r\n<p>Ju nuk keni pse të jeni ekspert në programim për të instaluar PrestaShop dhe për të filluar dizenjimin e dyqanit tuaj online.</p>\r\n<p>Sipas W3Tech, PrestaShop përdoret nga gati 1.4% e të gjitha faqeve të e-Commerce. Ajo preferohet nga bizneset e vogla bizneset e vogla.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop ka një ndërfaqe të thjeshtë për përdoruesin, me sistemin e menaxhimit të inventarit dhe me mirëmbajtjen së dyqaneve online. PrestaShop siguron një sistem menaxhimi për shumë shitës dyqani, me një navigim të lehtë për shitësit.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',633,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"PrestaShop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:716:\"<p>The PrestaShop may be a newer E-Commerce platform, but it is getting popular because of easy installation, accessibility, and provision of the amazing interface.</p>\r\n<p>You do not have to be technically sound to install its plugin and start designing your store.</p>\r\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/cm-prestashop/all/all\">W3Tech</a>, PrestaShop is used by nearly 1.4% of all the online shopping websites. It is quite beneficial for small businesses to start with it.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop has a user-friendly interface with seamless inventory management system and store maintenance process. It also provides a multi-vendor support system with easy navigation across the site.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',633,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(803,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,634,1567428079,1567427542,10,0,0,1279,'textpic','ZenCart','','','<p>Nëse nuk jeni një programues në Web, atëherë me ZenCart ju mund të rritni cilësinë e dyqanit tuaj online. ZenCart ka rreth 150,000 anëtarë mbështetës në komunitetin e saj. Sipas një studimi të fundit, ZenCart përdoret nga 0,1% e të gjitha faqeve të e-Commerce. ZenCart gëzon këto karakteristika:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Siguron një sistem të shkëlqyeshëm të administrimit të produkteve</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Krijon inventar të specializuar</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mban shitjet online</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Përbëhet nga modele që personalizohen</li> 	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fokusohet 100% në nevojat e klientit<br /> 	&nbsp;</li> </ul>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',634,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"ZenCart\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:621:\"<p>If you are not a skilled developer, then also with the usage of ZenCart, you can upscale your E-Commerce store. It has around 150,000 members in its support community. According to the <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/cm-zencart/all/all\">latest study</a>, ZenCart is used by 0.1% of all the online shopping websites. ZenCart includes the following features:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>Provides great product management system</li> 	<li>Creating specialized inventory</li> 	<li>Keeping sales at your fingertips</li> 	<li>It consists of customized templates</li> 	<li>100% focus on the customer needs</li> </ul>\r\n\r\n\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',634,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(804,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,635,1567428117,1567427542,10,0,0,1407,'textpic','Drupal','','','<p>Drupal ka një funksionalitet global dhe është i njohur si një sistem mjaft i fuqishëm. Drupal mund të integrohet lehtësisht me platformat e palëve të treta.</p>\r\n<p>Kjo platformë me kod të hapur është e ndërtuar në CMS, duke siguruar një sistem të fortë të menaxhimit të përmbajtjes. Drupal Commerce është duke u bërë një pretendent i fuqishëm në mesin e shitësve online.</p>\r\n<p>Sipas W3Tech, Drupal përdoret nga 3.5% e të gjithë faqeve aktuale në Web. Versioni i tij Drupal 8 përdoret nga 13.4% e përdoruesve.</p>\r\n<p>Zhvilluesit janë duke punuar për të lancuar në vitin 2020 versionin Drupal 9. Një shërbim tjetër i kësaj platforme është mbajtja shënim e historikut të porosive, faturave, arkëtimeve dhe pagesave.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',635,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:6:\"Drupal\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:723:\"<p>This platform has a global functionality and is known for its robust nature. Drupal can integrate with the third-party platforms without any hassle.</p>\r\n<p>This open-source platform is built on CMS so it provides a strong content management system. Even Drupal Commerce is becoming a powerful contender amongst the online retailers.</p>\r\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/cm-drupal/all/all\">W3Tech</a>, Drupal is used by 3.5% of all the present websites. Its version 8 is used by 13.4% of the users.</p>\r\n<p>The developers are working to release its version 9 by the year 2020. Another benefit of this platform is that it keeps tracks of the orders, invoices, receipts, and payments.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',635,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(805,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,636,1567428156,1567427542,10,0,0,1471,'textpic','OpenCart','','','<p>OpenCart është një nga platformat e njohura të e-Commerce. Ajo ka një ndërfaqe të shkëlqyeshme, të menaxhueshme me 20 porta për pagesat online, 8 mënyra transporti dhe 100 porta për procesin e transportit.</p>\r\n<p>Nëse kompania juaj nuk ka të punësuar ekspert të PHP, atëherë gjithashtu ju mund të zgjidhni këtë metodë.</p>\r\n<p>OpenCart e thjeshtë, funksionon shpejt në serverin tuaj, posedon plugins të shumta dhe ka tema të bollshme për të rregulluar dyqanin tuaj online.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',636,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:8:\"OpenCart\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:482:\"<p>This is one of the popular <strong>PHP E-Commerce</strong> platforms. It has a great manageable interface with 20 gateways for payment, 8 shipping methods, and 100 of gateways for shipping process.</p>\r\n<p>If your <strong>company</strong> does not have the most tech-savvy employees, then also you can opt for this method.</p>\r\n<p>It is simple, runs quickly on your server, possesses numerous plugins, and has plentiful themes to customize your online <strong>store</strong>.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',636,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(806,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,637,1567428180,1567427542,10,0,1,1503,'textpic','Si përfundim','','','<p>Këto 10 platforma që përmendëm më lart, janë më të mirat mundësi me kod të hapur. Ato do të ndryshojnë pamjen e dyqanit tuaj online, duke u integruar lehtësisht dhe me një kosto minimale.</p>\r\n<p>Ju madje mund të kërkoni për shërbime ndihmëse drejt agjencive me ekspertë të fushës, duke përmirësuar kështu imazhin e kompanisë tuaj për shitjet online.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'14','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,1,NULL,'',0,'',637,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"Conclusion\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"14\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:231:\"<p>These 10 best open-source E-Commerce platforms are going to change your online website look with easy integration and their cost-effective features.</p>\r\n<p>You can even hire some reputed agencies to work on your behalf too.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',637,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(807,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,728,1567506570,1567506551,11,0,0,160,'image','','','',NULL,0,0,0,0,1,750,0,2,0,0,0,'none',0,0,'','','','',0,0,1,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',728,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";s:5:\"image\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:1;s:6:\"header\";s:0:\"\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:1:\"0\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:750;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:4:\"none\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',728,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(808,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,620,1613030466,1567506551,11,0,0,320,'textpic','Le 10 migliori framework di e-commerce da non perdere nel 2021 ','','','<p>La maggior parte dei framework di e-commerce utilizzati attualmente sono economici o gratuiti. I framework open source<br /> sono preferite perché si offrono gratuite e possono essere gestite e sviluppate da persone esperte da tutto il mondo.<br /> I framework open source sono piene di funzionalità uniche e facili da sviluppare.</p>\r\n<p>In questo articolo c\'è un elenco con le 10 principali framework di e-commerce open source, da non perdere nel 2021.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'100','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',620,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:7:\"Preface\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:3:\"100\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1332:\"<p>An e-Commerce platform is a piece of software that allows you to build an online store and run a business online.</p>\r\n<p>Most of the <strong>eCommerce</strong> frameworks used are currently inexpensive or free. The open-source platforms are valuable as they are not only free but also managed and developed by experienced people across the globe.</p>\r\n<p>It is advisable to decide on the experience you require from your online store which may be a self-hosting or complete package at a small fee.</p>\r\n<p>People use open-source platforms as they are packed with unique features and developer-friendly.</p>\r\n<p>In this article, we will focus on the top 10 important open-source <strong>eCommerce</strong> platforms to watch out in 2020 and how to choose the right one for your business.</p>\r\n<p>It’s a difficult task for you to find the right eCommerce platform for your business.</p>\r\n<p><em><strong>What does open source mean?</strong></em><br /> Denoting software for which the original source code is made freely available and may be redistributed and modified.</p>\r\n<p>So, you don’t have to deal with vendor lock. All you need to do is figure out what your business goals are, here is a complete quick guideline that will help decide which open source is right for your <em><strong>eCommerce business</strong></em>.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',620,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(809,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,621,1612147893,1567506551,11,0,0,352,'textpic','Magento 2','','','<p>Magento si basa su PHP, che aiuta a costruire funzionalità scalabili. Questo framework include numerosi plug-in<br /> ed extensions che possono essere facilmente integrati con le app di terze parti.</p>\r\n<p>Magento è stato creato per gli esperti, per costruire un plugin di Magento si ricomincia da capo.</p>\r\n<p>L\'utente ha bisogno di esperienza nella programmazione PHP.<br /> Magento ha due versioni: Magento 1 e Magento 2.</p>\r\n<p>La versione Magento 2 è l\'ultimo sviluppo, in quanto la utilizzano oltre 200.000 venditori online.</p>\r\n<p>Questa versione offre strumenti per le funzionalità avanzate di marketing, gestione del catalogo e SEO.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,1,0,17,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',621,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:9:\"Magento 2\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1029:\"<p><a href=\"https://magento.com/\" title=\"Magento\">Magento</a>&nbsp;is one of the most popular <strong>eCommerce</strong> platforms in today’s market, build on open source technologies&nbsp;which provides online merchants with a flexible shopping cart system, provides more than 50 payment gateways, it is a&nbsp;<strong>PHP</strong>-based framework that helps in building scalable solutions.</p>\r\n<p>This platform comes packed with multiple plugins and extensions that can be easily integrated with the third-party apps.</p>\r\n<p>As it is built for the developers, so they do not have to start from scratch.</p>\r\n<p>The user needs expertise in <em><strong>PHP</strong></em>&nbsp;<em><strong>programming</strong></em>. The <strong>Magento</strong> had two versions <strong>Magento 1</strong> and <strong>Magento 2</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>The Magento 2 version is the latest development as more than 200,000 online retailers use it.</p>\r\n<p>This version offers tools to cover advanced marketing, catalogue management, and SEO needs.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',621,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(810,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,622,1612147927,1567506551,11,0,0,368,'textpic','WooCommerce','','','<p>WooCommerce è un plug-in di WordPress, con caratteristiche e funzionalità intuitive. Questo plug-in è gratuito, e rende enormi funzionalità estendibili.</p>\r\n<p>Se vuoi iniziare una perfetta esperienza della vendita online, WooCommerce è facilmente comprensibile e altamente raccomandato.</p>\r\n<p>WooCommerce offre molte opzioni che supportano la costruzione di un negozio fantastico con una maggiore flessibilità, perché è professionale, è semplice, possiede gli ultimi WooThemes di personalizzazione.</p>\r\n<p>WooCommerce collega tutti i principali gateway al tuo sito Web, e rende anche Stripe e PayPal come gateway di pagamento predefinito.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',622,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:11:\"WooCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:1028:\"<p><a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce</a> is a WordPress plugin that has user-friendly features and functionalities that can be integrated easily with your existing <strong>WordPress</strong> site.</p>\r\n<p>It is <strong>free</strong> to download and renders enormous extendible features.</p>\r\n<p>If you want to start a perfect <strong>E-Commerce</strong> startup up with a great website, then it is easily understandable and highest recommended.</p>\r\n<p>One of the most recommended open-source eCommerce platforms in the world, <strong>WooCommerce</strong> includes its own secure payment processor and shopping card.</p>\r\n<p>It provides plenty of options that support in building an amazing store with greater flexibility.</p>\r\n<p>It’s professional, simple, possess the latest WooThemes, and has many customization options.</p>\r\n<p>It connects all the major gateways to your website. It also renders <strong>Stripe</strong> and <strong>PayPal</strong> as the default <em>payment gateways</em>.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:1;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:17;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',622,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(811,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,628,1567507223,1567506551,11,0,0,376,'textpic','Aimeos','','','<p>Aimeos è una libreria PHP di e-commerce, con codice aperto, e che offre una serie di componenti per le applicazioni dei negozi online. Aimeos è integrato in componenti semplici da usare, disponibili per diversi framework. Le sue integrazioni esistenti includono:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>&nbsp;TYPO3 Web shop extension</li> 	<li>&nbsp;Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>&nbsp;Laravel E-Commerce</li> 	<li>&nbsp;Flow Online shop</li> 	<li>&nbsp;SlimPHP E-Commerce</li> </ul>\r\n<p>Le caratteristiche principali di questo framework consistono in una facile integrazione, in operazioni più veloci, in capacità multi-store, essendo altamente scalabile, flessibile, ottimizzata per dispositivi mobili e configurabile.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',628,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:6:\"Aimeos\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:643:\"<p>It is open-source PHP library and an E-Commerce framework offering a set of featured components for online shop applications. The Aimeos is integrated into simple to use components that are available for a wide range of frameworks. Its existing integrations include:</p>\r\n<ul> 	<li>TYPO3 Web shop extension</li> 	<li>Symfony E-Commerce bundle</li> 	<li>Laravel E-Commerce package</li> 	<li>Flow Online shop package</li> 	<li>SlimPHP E-Commerce package</li> </ul>\r\n<p>The main features of this platform consist of easy integration, faster operations, multi-store capability, highly scalable, flexible, mobile optimized, and configurable.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',628,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(812,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,630,1612147993,1567506551,11,0,0,380,'textpic','OsCommerce','','','<p>OsCommerce esiste da 15 anni. È vista come una vecchia opzione affidabile per molte piccole imprese e startup.</p>\r\n<p>Questo framework di e-commerce offre oltre 7.000 integrazioni gratuite con 13.000 negozi che sono costruite su basano su OsCommerce.</p>\r\n<p>Secondo uno studio, OsCommerce è l\'undicesimo framework più popolare tra i primi 1 milione di siti con codice aperto.</p>\r\n<p>I venditori online lo utilizzano per la sua facilità di progettazione di un negozio online ben gestito.</p>\r\n<p>OsCommerce si integra facilmente con tutte le app di terze parti, presentando il tuo sito online in molte lingue straniere.</p>\r\n<p>Esiste un gran numero di sviluppatori che può aiutarti per rendere più facile il tuo processo di sviluppo, e per di più, OsCommerce non è per niente difficile.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',630,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"OsCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:788:\"<p>OsCommerce is into the business for the last 15 years. It is seen as an old reliable option for many small businesses and startups to get seamless features.</p>\r\n<p>This E-Commerce platform renders more than 7,000 free integrations with 13,000 stores running on this platform.</p>\r\n<p>According to a <a href=\"https://trends.builtwith.com/shop/osCommerce\">study</a>, it is 11th most popular amongst Top 1 million sites in the open-source category.<br /> The online retailers use it for its ease to design a well-managed online shop.</p>\r\n<p>This platform easily integrates with all the third-party apps, presents your online site in multiple languages.<br /> You can find a vast number of community developers to ease out your development process, and OsCommerce is not all complex.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',630,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(813,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,631,1612148044,1567506551,11,0,0,382,'textpic','xtCommerce','','','<p>Questo è un nuovo framework di e-commerce open source utilizzata dalle case di business al giorno d\'oggi.</p>\r\n<p>Lo sviluppo in corso è fatto con questo framework per migliorare le sue funzionalità.</p>\r\n<p>xtCommerce aiuta i proprietari dei negozi a promuovere un numero illimitato di prodotti online.</p>\r\n<p>Puoi persino creare sottosezioni di questi prodotti per visualizzarli facilmente.</p>\r\n<p>Questa soluzione open source offre supporto multilingue, gestione di categorie illimitate, interfaccia facile da navigare, ecc.</p>\r\n<p>XtCommerce aiuta anche a fornire risposte Cart2Cart ai requisiti degli e-commerce. Se non sei a conoscenza dell\'integrazione di questo framework di e-commerce, puoi rivolgerti ai servizi correlati.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',631,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"xtCommerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:811:\"<p><a href=\"https://www.xt-commerce.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">xtCommerce</a>&nbsp;is open-source eCommerce Webshop Software (GPL). The ongoing development is done with this platform to enhance its functionalities.</p>\r\n<p>This platform helps the store owners to promote an unlimited number of products online. You can even create sub-sections of these products to display them with ease.</p>\r\n<p>This open-source solution renders multilingual support, manage unlimited categories, easy to navigate interface, etc.</p>\r\n<p>xtCommerce also helps in making Cart2Cart responses to the requirements of e-merchants.</p>\r\n<p>If you are not aware of integrating this E-Commerce platform, then you can outsource the related services.</p>\r\n<p>XtCommerce offer solutions for every eCommerce business type.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',631,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(814,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,632,1612148080,1567506551,11,0,0,383,'textpic','WP E-Commerce','','','<p>Questo plugin è \"la soluzione di e-commerce\" per WordPress.</p>\r\n<p>Gli sviluppatori hanno scaricato il WP E-Commerce<br /> più di 3 milioni di volte. Il codice di questo plugin di WordPress è abbastanza semplice.</p>\r\n<p>Se sei bravo in HTML e CSS, tu puoi gestire questo plugin con la massima facilità.</p>\r\n<p>I venditori online possono ottenere un supporto dalla agenzia di sviluppo WordPress o rivolgersi alla comunità di sviluppatori online. Gli esempi di WP E-Commerce sono Mayrun, MollyMeg e Cronut.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',632,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:13:\"WP E-Commerce\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:853:\"<p>This plugin boasts as the “original E-Commerce solution” for WordPress. The developers have downloaded the WP E-Commerce more than 3 million times, this means that many online shoppers are familiar with this plugin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>WP-ECommerce has some pre-installed payment gateways such as, PayPal - Express, Google, Checkout etc.</p>\r\n<p>The coding for this WordPress plugin is quite simple.&nbsp;You only have to be good to HTML and CSS, and you can handle this plugin with utmost ease.</p>\r\n<p>The online retailers can take support from the reputed WordPress development agency or can turn to the large community of online developers for support.</p>\r\n<p>The examples of <a href=\"https://wpecommerce.org/\" target=\"_blank\">WP E-Commer</a><a href=\"https://wpecommerce.org/\" target=\"_blank\">c</a>e are Mayrun’s Goods, MollyMeg, and Cronut.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',632,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(815,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,633,1612149374,1567506551,11,0,0,639,'textpic','PrestaShop','','','<p>PrestaShop è un nuovo framework di e-commerce, ma sta diventando popolare grazie alla facilità d\'installazione, accessibilità e alla straordinaria interfaccia.</p>\r\n<p>Non è necessario essere un tecnico per installare PrestaShop e per iniziare a progettare il tuo negozio.</p>\r\n<p>Secondo W3Tech, PrestaShop è utilizzato da quasi l\'1,4% di tutti i siti Web di shopping online. Questo plugin è il preferito per le piccole imprese.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop ha un\'interfaccia intuitiva con un sistema di gestione dell\'inventario e di manutenzione del punto vendita.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop offre un sistema di supporto multi-vendor, con una facile navigazione all\'interno del sito.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','','','',0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,2,NULL,'',0,'',633,'a:31:{s:5:\"CType\";s:7:\"textpic\";s:6:\"colPos\";i:0;s:6:\"header\";s:10:\"PrestaShop\";s:13:\"header_layout\";s:2:\"12\";s:15:\"header_position\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";i:0;s:11:\"header_link\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"subheader\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"bodytext\";s:790:\"<p>The <a href=\"https://www.prestashop.com/en\" target=\"_top\">PrestaShop</a> may be a newer E-Commerce platform, but it is getting popular because of easy installation, accessibility, and provision of the amazing interface.</p>\r\n<p>You do not have to be technically sound to install its plugin and start designing your store.</p>\r\n<p>According to <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/details/cm-prestashop/all/all\" target=\"_blank\">W3Tech</a>, PrestaShop is used by nearly 1.4% of all the online shopping websites. It is quite beneficial for small businesses to start with it.</p>\r\n<p>PrestaShop has a user-friendly interface with seamless inventory management system and store maintenance process. It also provides a multi-vendor support system with easy navigation across the site.</p>\";s:5:\"image\";i:0;s:10:\"imagewidth\";i:0;s:11:\"imageheight\";i:0;s:11:\"imageborder\";i:0;s:11:\"imageorient\";i:0;s:9:\"imagecols\";i:2;s:10:\"image_zoom\";i:0;s:6:\"layout\";i:0;s:11:\"frame_class\";s:7:\"default\";s:18:\"space_before_class\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"space_after_class\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"sectionIndex\";i:1;s:9:\"linkToTop\";i:0;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";i:0;s:6:\"hidden\";i:0;s:9:\"starttime\";i:0;s:7:\"endtime\";i:0;s:8:\"fe_group\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"editlock\";i:0;s:10:\"categories\";i:0;s:14:\"rowDescription\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"l18n_parent\";i:0;}',633,'','','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0),(816,65,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,634,1612149414,1567506551,11,0,0,767,'textpic','ZenCart','','','<p>Anche se non sei uno sviluppatore esperto, con