o mention more...</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(1066,120,0,0,0,0,0,1582036638,0,0,1582025921,1582024868,13,0,0,1792,'textpic','CONCLUSION','','','<p>Take in consideration all of the above risks, and &nbsp;carefully choose the outsourcing vendor. India is not the only one:&nbsp;As entrepreneur it is up to you to decide where to outsource your work.<br /> Locations like&nbsp;<a href=\"https://w3development.net/outsource-web-development-eastern-europe\" rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Eastern Europe</a>, the Middle East, USA or Australia, offers competitive outsourcing services and are a must to be consider.</p>\r\n\r\n',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N