 rel=\"noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">report in Apr2 of 2019</a>&nbsp;by talent assessment company Aspiring Minds shows a grimmer picture of the ability of IT engineering graduates in India.</p>\r\n<p>Only 10 percent, the report says, have adequate coding skills. Only between 3 and 4 percent are fit to fill roles like product engineer or startup engineer. The report also states that only 2.5 percent of Indian engineers possess skills in the field of artificial intelligence, only 4.5 percent are skilled in data engineering.</p>\r\n<p>From the above statistics, the probability of finding a good Indian developer is very low.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'12','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'a:30:{s:5:\"CType\";N;s:6:\"colPos\";N;s:6:\"header\";N;s:13:\"header_layout\";N;s:15:\"header_position\";N;s:4:\"date\";N;s:11:\"header_link\";N;s:9:\"subheader\";N;s:8:\"bodytext\";N;s:5:\"image\";N;s:10:\"imagewidth\";N;s:11:\"imageheight\";N;s:11:\"imageborder\";N;s:11:\"imageorient\";N;s:9:\"imagecols\";N;s:10:\"image_zoom\";N;s:6:\"layout\";N;s:11:\"frame_class\";N;s:18:\"space_before_class\";N;s:17:\"space_after_class\";N;s:12:\"sectionIndex\";N;s:9:\"linkToTop\";N;s:16:\"sys_language_uid\";N;s:6:\"hidden\";N;s:9:\"starttime\";N;s:7:\"endtime\";N;s:8:\"fe_group\";N;s:8:\"editlock\";N;s:10:\"categories\";N;s:14:\"rowDescription\";N;}',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(1151,123,0,0,0,0,0,1583094324,0,0,1582803255,1582803255,13,0,0,1280,'textpic','Time Zone Differences','','','<p>Outsourcing to India can be difficult due to the time difference between India and western countries. With about a 12 hour difference with MST (Mountain Standard Time) it is very difficult to find the right time to speak.</p>',0,0,0,0,0,0,0,2,0,0,0,'default',0,0,'','',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'','','',0,'0','',1,0,NULL,0,'','',0,0,0,0,NULL,'',0,'',0,'',0,NULL,'','',NULL,124,0,0,0,NULL,0,'',NULL,0,0,0,0),(1153,123,0,0,0,0,0,1583094324,0,0,